-->Multiplayer<!--]--></button><button class="bg-[--_bg-color,var(--color-button-bg)] text-nowrap border-[--_bg-color,var(--surface-5)] border-[1px] border-solid px-2 py-1 leading-none rounded-full font-normal text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[--_color,var(--color-secondary)] [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 [&amp;&gt;svg]:h-4 [&amp;&gt;svg]:w-4 transition-transform active:scale-[0.95] cursor-pointer hover:underline"><!--[-->Optimization<!--]--></button><!--]--></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-3 card flex-card" data-v-5c9cce00><h2 class="text-lg m-0">Creators</h2><div class="flex flex-col gap-3 font-semibold"><!----><!--[--><!--]--></div></div><!----><div class="card flex-card" data-v-5c9cce00><h2 data-v-5c9cce00>Details</h2><div class="details-list" data-v-5c9cce00><div class="details-list__item" data-v-5c9cce00><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="lucide lucide-book-text" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" data-v-5c9cce00><path d="M4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2H20v20H6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H20M8 7h6M8 11h8"></path></svg><div data-v-5c9cce00>Licensed <span class="text-link hover:underline" data-v-5c9cce00>ARR</span></div></div><!----><div class="details-list__item" data-v-5c9cce00><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" data-v-5c9cce00><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2"></path></svg><div data-v-5c9cce00>Published 3 years ago</div></div><!----><!----></div></div></div><div class="normal-page__content" data-v-5c9cce00><div class="overflow-x-auto" data-v-5c9cce00><nav class="relative flex w-fit overflow-x-auto rounded-full bg-bg-raised p-1 text-sm font-bold drop-shadow-xl border border-solid border-surface-4 mb-4" data-v-5c9cce00 style="--v62a4961a:0ms;--v39e38429:0ms;--v23d6dde0:0ms;--v0fa5b2f6:0ms;" data-v-e8ae1d02><!--[--><a aria-current="page" href="/modpack/medieval-mc-forge-mmc4" class="router-link-active router-link-exact-active button-animation z-[1] flex flex-row items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 focus:rounded-full rounded-full bg-button-bgSelected" style="" data-v-e8ae1d02><!----><span class="text-nowrap text-button-textSelected" data-v-e8ae1d02>Description</span></a><a href="/modpack/medieval-mc-forge-mmc4/gallery" class="button-animation z-[1] flex flex-row items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 focus:rounded-full" style="" data-v-e8ae1d02><!----><span class="text-nowrap text-contrast" data-v-e8ae1d02>Gallery</span></a><a href="/modpack/medieval-mc-forge-mmc4/changelog" class="button-animation z-[1] flex flex-row items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 focus:rounded-full" style="" data-v-e8ae1d02><!----><span class="text-nowrap text-contrast" data-v-e8ae1d02>Changelog</span></a><a href="/modpack/medieval-mc-forge-mmc4/versions" class="button-animation z-[1] flex flex-row items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 focus:rounded-full" style="" data-v-e8ae1d02><!----><span class="text-nowrap text-contrast" data-v-e8ae1d02>Versions</span></a><!--]--><!----></nav></div><section class="normal-page__content"><div class="card"><div class="markdown-body"><p><img src="https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/bed0adec645cc7795ce93fd9e796f505e14646fb.jpeg" alt="In gold and grey text, &quot;MEDIEVAL MINECRAFT&quot; is displayed infront of a screenshot of the Minecraft Overworld. The background image has a tree with purple leaves on both sides."></p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/785d3640a720d7e56cba3a6e2bbcdc37f34cf7e1.png" alt="In all-caps bold text, the word &quot;FEATURES&quot;."></p>
<p>⚔️ Full parity with <a href="https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/medieval-mc-mmc4" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Curseforge Version</a></p>
<p>⚔️ Completely Overhauled World Generation (<a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/biomes-o-plenty">Biomes o' Plenty</a>, <a href="https://modrinth.com/datapack/geophilic">Geophilic</a>, <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/ecologics">Ecologics</a>)</p>
<p>⚔️ Thousands of NEW Dungeons &amp; Structures (<a href="https://modrinth.com/datapack/wabi-sabi-structures">Wabi-Sabi Structures</a>, <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/when-dungeons-arise">When Dungeons Arise</a>, <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/towns-and-towers">Towns and Towers</a>)</p>
<p>⚔️ Grow Your Own Kingdom (<a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/minecolonies">Minecolonies</a>, <a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/stylecolonies" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Stylecolonies</a>)</p>
<p>⚔️ Explore Magical Dimensions (<a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/the-twilight-forest" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">The Twilight Forest</a>, <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/aether">The Aether</a> &amp; Addons, <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/betterend">BetterEnd</a>)</p>
<p>⚔️ Fully Optimized with Shader Support</p>
<p>⚔️ Overhauled Stronghold &amp; Fortresses</p>
<p>⚔️ Powerful Bosses and Mythical Creatures (<a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/l_enders-cataclysm">L_Ender's Cataclysm</a>, <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/ice-and-fire-dragons">Ice and Fire: Dragons</a>)</p>
<p>⚔️ In-depth Magic Mods (<a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/irons-spells-n-spellbooks">Iron's Spells 'n Spellbooks </a>, <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/ars-nouveau/">Ars Nouveau</a>, <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/eidolonrepraised">Eidolon: Repraised</a>, <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/wizards-reborn">Wizard's Reborn</a>)</p>
<p>⚔️ Stamina, Thirst and Temperature System (<a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/survive">Survive</a>)</p>
<p>⚔️ Simple Quests to Guide You</p>
<p>⚔️ QoL Features such as <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/waystones">Waystones</a> and <a href="https://modrinth.com/mod/travelersbackpack">Upgradeable Backpacks</a></p>
<p>⚔️ An Immersive Medieval RPG Experience</p>
<p>⚔️ Built-in, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tLTC6wYcWVM" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Free World Sharing</a></p>
