s, or have suggestions for improvements:\n\n- Open an issue on the [GitHub Issue Tracker](https://github.com/Choculaterie/LitematicDownloader/issues)\n- Or join the [Discord Server](https://discord.choculaterie.com) to chat directly with me and the community\n\nWhen reporting issues, please include:\n- Your Minecraft version\n- Fabric version\n- List of installed mods\n- Any relevant crash logs or game logs","2025-04-14T01:10:56.512351Z","2026-05-18T00:25:42.905930Z","2025-06-17T06:38:52.930199Z","2025-05-08T23:36:41.496651Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},65271,68,[157,175,303],[279,288],[346],[30510,30511,30512,30513,30514,30515,30516,30517,30518,30519,30520,30521,30522,30523,30524,30525,30526,30527,30528,30529],"cl0WtiXL","igR9dFYU","O4XxxSAK","e9aUONyS","Ggc19ktW","FQPUZtfl","feQ5PbAY","HoWyO6Bd","uHtCtBp4","dafvdfdh","GwOEyr3b","BJN4xEUm","5F1qIRJi","KtZoMyrt","rNZ93smJ","Uq93OJFD","1QAhEes7","VMgnwErP","sZpXHAG0","xrp3zQz7","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3G2Q24n/0e94530bf9e213b008b0abf938970726b32de1dd.png","https://github.com/Choculaterie/LitematicDownloader/issues","https://github.com/Choculaterie/LitematicDownloader","https://discord.choculaterie.com/",[30535],{"id":3149,"platform":3150,"url":30536},"https://ko-fi.com/choculat",[30538,30543,30548],{"url":30539,"raw_url":30540,"featured":849,"title":30541,"description":3592,"created":30542,"ordering":29981},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3G2Q24n/images/875e5e2445b36ef8129996893d59bdd817b1a4d4_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3G2Q24n/images/875e5e2445b36ef8129996893d59bdd817b1a4d4.png","Download Page & Details","2025-12-13T01:35:49.876688Z",{"url":30544,"raw_url":30545,"featured":439,"title":30546,"description":3592,"created":30547,"ordering":29987},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3G2Q24n/images/14e0c8e4aa884ef1acf9d9841c8ac8adc5ec37f6_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3G2Q24n/images/14e0c8e4aa884ef1acf9d9841c8ac8adc5ec37f6.png","File Manager Page","2025-12-13T01:35:25.987099Z",{"url":30549,"raw_url":30550,"featured":439,"title":30551,"description":3592,"created":30552,"ordering":29993},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3G2Q24n/images/50093c6cba984ea293c589a541ccd086646c4fc3_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3G2Q24n/images/50093c6cba984ea293c589a541ccd086646c4fc3.png","Details & Replace Any Blocks","2026-02-06T22:11:12.219506Z",14281121,"tCd9u4ad",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":30037,"game_versions":30556,"id":30557,"slug":30558,"project_type":31,"team":30559,"organization":3592,"title":30560,"description":30561,"body":30562,"body_url":3592,"published":30563,"updated":30564,"approved":30565,"queued":30566,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":30567,"downloads":30568,"followers":29987,"categories":30569,"additional_categories":30570,"loaders":30571,"versions":30572,"icon_url":30581,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":30582,"donation_urls":30583,"gallery":30584,"color":30590,"thread_id":30591,"monetization_status":30002},[760,655,559,499,487],"T3Tk2sqY","jarvispvp","O5xrHIkr","Jarvis","Items durability alerts, armor durability alerts, health bar, damage indicators, health monitor with JARVIS voice.","\u003Ch1>JarvisPvP – Smart PvP Alerts and Combat Awareness\u003C/h1>\n\n\u003Cp>JarvisPvP is a combat-focused assistant built for players who want faster reactions, cleaner awareness, and less guesswork in every fight. It helps you stay locked in with clear warnings, a stylish in-world health bar, and real-time combat information that matters when fights get intense.\u003C/p>\n\n\u003Cp>⭐ Built for PvP\u003Cbr>\n⭐ Fast, clear, non-spammy alerts\u003Cbr>\n⭐ English and Spanish support\u003Cbr>\n⭐ Works great for practice, duels, Crystal PvP, KitPvP, and SMP combat\u003C/p>\n\n\u003Ch2>Top Features\u003C/h2>\n\n\u003Ch3>Item Durability Alerts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Get warned before your weapon, tool, shield, or other important item is about to break\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Low durability and critical durability warnings help you swap in time\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Designed to keep you from losing fights because of surprise breaks\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\n\u003Ch3>Armor Durability Alerts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Tracks your armor condition during combat and warns you before it becomes a real problem\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Includes compromised, low, critical, and near-breaking armor warnings\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Helps you react before your gear fails in the middle of a fight\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\n\u003Ch3>In-World Health Bar\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Shows a clean health bar beside players in the world for quick visual tracking\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Easy to read, combat-friendly, and designed to stay useful without cluttering your screen\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Customizable to match your preferred look and spacing\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\n\u003Ch3>Health Alerts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Low health warning\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Critical health warning\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Alerts trigger at the right moments without constant repetition\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Built to keep you informed without flooding you during hectic fights\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\n\u003Ch2>More Combat Features\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Totem alerts\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Golden apple alerts\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Ender pearl alerts\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>XP bottle alerts\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Resource awareness for faster decision-making\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Combat mode for focused PvP-only behavior\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Optional crit indicator\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Combat boss bar\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Action bar alerts\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Optional title and subtitle warnings\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Audio alerts with English and Spanish support\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>In-game config menu with live changes\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Keybinds for quick control\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Clean, lightweight, and performance-conscious design\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\n\u003Ch2>Why Players Use JarvisPvP\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Stay ahead of armor breaks and item breaks\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Track enemy health more easily during pressure fights\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>React faster to danger without staring at your inventory\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Get useful warnings without annoying spam\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Keep your attention on PvP instead of micromanaging everything manually\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\n\u003Ch2>Perfect For\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Practice PvP\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Crystal PvP\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>KitPvP\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>SMP PvP\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Duels\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Competitive servers\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\n\u003Ch2>Simple and Focused\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>JarvisPvP is made for awareness, not automation. It gives you the information you need to react faster, protect your gear, and stay in control when every second matters.\u003C/p>\n\n\u003Cp>Fight smarter. React faster. Stay alive longer.\u003C/p>\n","2026-04-08T16:57:04.105323Z","2026-05-04T05:38:48.621128Z","2026-04-22T02:29:16.751342Z","2026-04-08T17:07:18.448397Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},410,[134,303],[30,105,185],[346],[30573,30574,30575,30576,30577,30578,30579,30580],"Wz5I0Wyz","LWIdGOQ1","ealinawz","ffbOdhVA","ygO7oPfP","zyMvZYsu","Kdu0aXh8","VBuhE6it","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3Tk2sqY/0a2fc27723db823c17aeb0d02caf8ea590cfb595.png","https://discord.gg/K8AbzbarGu",[],[30585],{"url":30586,"raw_url":30587,"featured":849,"title":30560,"description":30588,"created":30589,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3Tk2sqY/images/36015209ba644b06b5df3f897cdc939eae7f8e20_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3Tk2sqY/images/36015209ba644b06b5df3f897cdc939eae7f8e20.png","Jarvis Active + Lunar Client","2026-04-08T17:05:05.685899Z",310484,"ZR2lp6Er",{"client_side":29949,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":30593,"id":30594,"slug":30595,"project_type":31,"team":30596,"organization":3592,"title":30597,"description":30598,"body":30599,"body_url":3592,"published":30600,"updated":30601,"approved":30602,"queued":30603,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":30604,"downloads":30605,"followers":30606,"categories":30607,"additional_categories":30608,"loaders":30609,"versions":30610,"icon_url":30617,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":30618,"donation_urls":30619,"gallery":30620,"color":30630,"thread_id":30631,"monetization_status":30002},[604,559],"T4TaBo4H","photocraft-dp","PBVNnOFp","Photocraft","A functional \"instant\" camera that generates map art of the player's viewpoint","### **Warning**  \n#### **This datapack uses experimental features!**  \n#### **Please make a backup before adding this pack to an existing world!** \n\n\u003Ciframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/AfcoarzWisk\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen>\u003C/iframe>\n\n### **Resource Pack Required**\n#### To find the relevant resource pack, go to the page for the specific datapack [version](https://modrinth.com/datapack/photocraft-dp/versions) you are trying to install!\n\n# Photocraft Datapack\n\n![Animated comparison of photographed region and resulting photograph](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/46cc0f1f3218e1e99e1087b2901571e6f5bace23.gif)  \n\nThis datapack adds a camera that can be used to create map-art \"photos\" of the world.  \nThere are two items and recipes added to the game - the camera itself, and photo paper.  \n\nYou can craft a Camera with 3 Black Carpet, 2 Iron Ingots, 2 Redstone, 1 Spyglass, and 1 Lightning Rod:  \n![Crafting Recipe for Camera](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3aea455c1586c4574ff255d9d4e4de3dbf879711.png)\n\nYou can craft 4 pieces of Photo Paper with 3 Resin, 3 Paper, 1 Cyan Dye, 1 Yellow Dye, and 1 Magenta Dye:  \n![Crafting Recipe for Photo Paper](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/67390af0ff14a083de57c97b67939ccf3a359a22.png)\n\nTo use the camera, click and hold the use-item button. This will pull up a viewfinder that will provide a frame of what will be included in the photo. Releasing the use-item button will place the camera in the world.  \n![Example of Viewfinder](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/66d0b3f55e930c8e495ee793af78f2b3857cac99_0.webp)\n\nTo take a photo, click the use-item button on the camera while holding a piece of photo paper. The camera will start emitting smoke particles and the lights on the back of the camera will start turning on, showing photo progress.  \n![A Camera generating a photo](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/bb9d8fd093d0f5c3a6c7f1800f631dd64e049930_0.webp)\n\nWhen the camera is done exposing the photo, the lights on the back will turn green and the camera will play a sound.  \n![A camera that is done generating a photo](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/75240d36ae1292da9aeee9c35cd98a1c8a4c6537.png)\n\nRight click the camera with an empty hand to retrieve the final photo.  \n![A finalized photo](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/17e3a61364318e395e390b66782c2b03e96d12bb.png)\n\nAt any point, other than when retrieving a photo, left-clicking the camera will cause it to break, dropping a camera. Any photo that is stored in the camera **will be lost** if it is not retrieved first!","2025-10-28T03:40:46.770547Z","2025-12-11T17:41:24.338579Z","2025-11-13T20:02:00.424181Z","2025-11-13T18:30:54.574676Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},1486,21,[134],[275,303],[342,346,354,385,409],[30611,30612,30613,30614,30615,30616],"NBuCParu","UCPYI1yw","ScEjRstf","hL7TIrTX","mPXBhIAx","FT19i6As","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4TaBo4H/477df49789573cf4d44f86b741f5efbfbd4c8f2d.png","https://discord.com/invite/Vr9vfP6EqH",[],[30621,30625],{"url":30622,"raw_url":30622,"featured":849,"title":30623,"description":3592,"created":30624,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4TaBo4H/images/17e3a61364318e395e390b66782c2b03e96d12bb.png","Final Photo","2025-11-13T18:29:51.139806Z",{"url":30626,"raw_url":30627,"featured":439,"title":30628,"description":3592,"created":30629,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4TaBo4H/images/66d0b3f55e930c8e495ee793af78f2b3857cac99_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4TaBo4H/images/66d0b3f55e930c8e495ee793af78f2b3857cac99.png","Photographed Area","2025-11-13T18:30:19.031828Z",293900,"ioeX5O55",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":30633,"id":30634,"slug":30635,"project_type":31,"team":30636,"organization":3592,"title":30637,"description":30638,"body":30639,"body_url":3592,"published":30640,"updated":30641,"approved":30642,"queued":30643,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":30644,"downloads":30361,"followers":30075,"categories":30645,"additional_categories":30646,"loaders":30647,"versions":30648,"icon_url":30650,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":30651,"gallery":30652,"color":30683,"thread_id":30684,"monetization_status":30002},[841],"T3VkaVYl","the-bob-mod!","zusQaErP","The Bob Mod!","The Bob Mod adds, you guessed it, Bob! Bob can fly around his bob castle, and his portal room to the Bob dimension. The Bob chicken is also added, and is a brand new boss to fight!","# Whats in the mod, anyway?\n> Bob\n-  Bob flies around randomly, and when killed, drops bob's brains\n> Bob Portal Room\n- The Bob Portal Room spawns in the bob biome and lets you access the Bob dimension.\n> Bob Chicken\n- The Bob Chicken is a new boss, and has a LOT lot of health.\n> Bob Biome\n- The Bob Biome is a biome that is covered in waxed weathered cut copper stairs, and has 3 layers of diamond blocks underneath.\n> Bob Dimension\n- The Bob Dimension is covered with bob blocks. That's it.\n> Taco\n- The Taco has a nutrition value of 9 and a saturation of 1.1.\n> Bucket of Milk, but beter\n- The Bucket of milk, but better is a placeable milk bucket. Does not rid effects, however.\n> Bobcatsle\n- The Bobcaltle is a randomly spawning castle. Not much to it.\n\n**And much more!**\n\n\n\n\n# If you have any suggestions, comment on this video! \nhttps://www.youtube.com/shorts/AD8aqdvozXE\n*Some changes have been made, however.\n\n\n# This mod is also avalible on MCreator:\n## https://mcreator.net/modification/122253/bob-mod\n\n## So, why download?\n\n\u003Cdetails>\n\u003Csummary>Spoiler\u003C/summary>\n\n> It's fun, just trust\n\n\u003C/details>\n\n","2026-06-06T14:59:03.634805Z","2026-06-06T15:02:36.899037Z","2026-06-13T19:16:23.832084Z","2026-06-10T22:23:33.787695Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},[93],[],[385],[30649],"jCqrFVjZ","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3VkaVYl/1e4afdf83945bfe4dba7d49c1746d3793fd2d061_96.webp",[],[30653,30659,30665,30671,30677],{"url":30654,"raw_url":30655,"featured":439,"title":30656,"description":30657,"created":30658,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3VkaVYl/images/2a8d353228f0c008c0752f168435b281081ce65d_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3VkaVYl/images/2a8d353228f0c008c0752f168435b281081ce65d.png","Bob Biome","The Bob Biome is covered with Waxed Weathered Cut Copper Stairs, with diamond blocks underneath.","2026-06-10T01:27:22.439933Z",{"url":30660,"raw_url":30661,"featured":439,"title":30662,"description":30663,"created":30664,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3VkaVYl/images/3756b2de5aed6ac7d99f3fe8810efa5ce88f3f62_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3VkaVYl/images/3756b2de5aed6ac7d99f3fe8810efa5ce88f3f62.png","Bob Portal Room","The Bob Portal Room spawns a Bob Portal with Bob loot inside the chests.","2026-06-10T01:28:31.285979Z",{"url":30666,"raw_url":30667,"featured":439,"title":30668,"description":30669,"created":30670,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3VkaVYl/images/4d8be6821fefbb1fdde8d7ae67c74a55a57f35cf_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3VkaVYl/images/4d8be6821fefbb1fdde8d7ae67c74a55a57f35cf.png","Bob","Bob flys around your world and drops 'Bob's Brains' when killed.","2026-06-10T01:23:32.412975Z",{"url":30672,"raw_url":30673,"featured":439,"title":30674,"description":30675,"created":30676,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3VkaVYl/images/58d130fe1ebdaf0f04dadb835a1a7963fbb673b8_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3VkaVYl/images/58d130fe1ebdaf0f04dadb835a1a7963fbb673b8.png","Bob Portal","The Bob Portal takes you to the Bob Dimension.","2026-06-10T01:29:20.376477Z",{"url":30678,"raw_url":30679,"featured":439,"title":30680,"description":30681,"created":30682,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3VkaVYl/images/6cefa492dba6fb3f157d35f6d2a0ce7c7c6b0a91_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3VkaVYl/images/6cefa492dba6fb3f157d35f6d2a0ce7c7c6b0a91.png","Crown","The crown","2026-06-10T00:57:19.357604Z",13304836,"4hQnqUcP",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":30686,"id":30687,"slug":30688,"project_type":31,"team":30689,"organization":3592,"title":30690,"description":30691,"body":30692,"body_url":3592,"published":30693,"updated":30694,"approved":30695,"queued":30696,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":30697,"downloads":30701,"followers":29987,"categories":30702,"additional_categories":30703,"loaders":30704,"versions":30705,"icon_url":30707,"issues_url":30708,"source_url":30709,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":30710,"gallery":30711,"color":30717,"thread_id":30718,"monetization_status":30002},[841],"T3CecRuS","createphantom","2yqM00F2","Create：Phantom","Add package delivery functionality to Phantom.","# Welcome to Create Phantom\n\nCreate: Phantom expands the package logistics system of Create, adding airborne package delivery and portable multi-channel stock management.\n\nSend packages to a Phantom Port, launch Cargo Phantoms from belts, and manage multiple logistics networks from a single portable ticker.\n\n## Items\n\n### Cargo Phantom\n\nA small airborne courier that can carry a **Create package**.\n\nThe crago phantom can be launched from a belt when the belt is fast enough and has enough effective runway length. After delivery, the empty phantom can return to a phantom port or to the player.\n\n### Phantom Port\n\nA package port for **Cargo Phantom** logistics.\n\nIt can store packages and cargo phantoms, dispatch matching packages through its special output side, receive arriving packages.\n\n### Tunable Portable Stock Ticker\n\nA portable stock ticker with **switchable storage channels**.\n\nUse it to open a linked logistics network from your inventory. It can hold up to **six** Storage Channel Extension Cards, allowing one item to switch between multiple logistics networks.\n\n### Storage Channel Extension Card\n\nStores a **logistics network frequency** and **package addresses**.\n\n## Tips\n\n### Takeoff Rules\n\nCargo phantoms do not launch from every belt. Takeoff depends on both the belt's **absolute speed** and the remaining **effective belt length** in the belt's movement direction.\n\nEffective belt length means the number of belt segments from the Mini Phantom's insertion position to the belt output end. A long belt can still fail to launch if the Mini Phantom is inserted too close to the exit.\n\n| belt speed | belt length | take off |\n| :---:  | :---:  | :---: |\n| `\u003C 16` | — | No |\n| `16 - 31.99` | `>=6` | Yes |\n| `32 - 63.99` | `>=5` | Yes |\n| `64 - 127.99` | `>=4` | Yes |\n| `128 - 255.99` | `>=3` | Yes |\n| `>= 256` | `>=2` | Yes |\n\n### Phantom Port Output\n\nPlace an andesite funnel on the Phantom Port's special side and connect it to a belt below the funnel. The Phantom Port will provide a cargo phantom with package only when a valid target can be found.\n\n### Manual launch Cargo Phantom\n\nPlace the cargo phantom with package on the ground and use a firework to take off.\n\n### Package Addresses\n\nPhantom Port address matching follows Create package address rules. Text after `//` is treated as a comment and ignored by Create: Phantom address matching.\n\n## Compatibility\n\n### Create: Fluid Logistics\n\nThe Tunable Portable Stock Ticker can display and request fluid.\n\n## Others\n\nIf you want to help translate this mod, make a pull request with the translation files.\n","2026-06-04T12:38:57.666777Z","2026-06-04T12:43:10.331418Z","2026-06-05T00:38:00.137873Z","2026-06-04T12:46:19.171960Z",{"id":30698,"name":30699,"url":30700},"BSD-3-Clause","BSD 3-Clause \"New\" or \"Revised\" License","https://github.com/yision1/CreatePhantom?tab=License-1-ov-file",78,[279,297,303],[],[385],[30706],"IPo7v81g","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3CecRuS/e409d9127fc9045c08deaa0b733254364172b6de_96.webp","https://github.com/yision1/CreatePhantom/issues","https://github.com/yision1/CreatePhantom",[],[30712],{"url":30713,"raw_url":30714,"featured":439,"title":30715,"description":3592,"created":30716,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3CecRuS/images/5c30dc032665658e467c97cf5a8e07060b1879a4_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3CecRuS/images/5c30dc032665658e467c97cf5a8e07060b1879a4.png","take off","2026-06-04T12:45:59.680551Z",5201781,"piCDdKQK",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":30037,"game_versions":30720,"id":30721,"slug":30722,"project_type":12,"team":30723,"organization":3592,"title":30724,"description":30725,"body":30726,"body_url":3592,"published":30727,"updated":30728,"approved":30729,"queued":30730,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":30731,"downloads":30735,"followers":29987,"categories":30736,"additional_categories":30737,"loaders":30738,"versions":30739,"icon_url":30743,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":30744,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":30745,"gallery":30746,"color":30753,"thread_id":30754,"monetization_status":30002},[1214,1181,1172,1136,1097],"T3lVgdjw","minewar","TrYjBi6q","MineWar","This resourcepack replaces the vanilla music with Warcraft music.","# Caution\nI advise you to use [Constant Music](https://modrinth.com/mod/constant-music) to remove long pauses when the music does not play.\n## Description and Music List\nThe resourcepack was created for more atmosphere when playing with the [Reign of Nether RTS](https://modrinth.com/mod/reign-of-nether-rts) mod.\n\n[Listen music on YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/shorts/DIuaD1GHLDk)\n### Warcraft III: Reign Of Chaos\n- Reign of Chaos\n- Comradeship\n- Sad Mistery\n- Blackrock & Roll\n- Lordaeron Fall\n- Frostmourne\n- Bloodlust\n- Doomhammer's Legacy\n- Temporary Alliances\n- Blight\n- Arcane Echoes\n- Carrion Waves\n- Arrival At Kalimdor\n- Awakening\n- Rise Of The Ancients\n- Cinematic Suite\n- Credits\n### Warcraft III: Frozen Throne\n- Main Screen\n- Last Days Of The Scourge\n- King Arthas Of Lordaeron\n- In Pursuit Of Illidan\n- Vengeance Of The Blood Elves\n- The Orcish Hordes\n- The Night Elves' Song\n- Last Days Of The Alliance\n### World of Warcraft\n- Legacy\n- Echoes of the Past\n- A Call To Arms\n- Elwynn Forest\n- Dun Morogh\n- Burning Steppes\n- The Shaping of the World\n- Orgrimmar\n### WoW: Burning Crusade\n- The Burning Legion\n### WoW: Wrath of the Lich King\n- Wrath of the Lich King","2024-10-19T20:41:46.577733Z","2024-10-20T13:51:24.713654Z","2024-10-23T04:26:10.432346Z","2024-10-20T03:54:42.886198Z",{"id":30732,"name":30733,"url":30734},"Apache-2.0","Apache License 2.0","https://spdx.org/licenses/Apache-2.0.html?utm_source=blog.modrinth.com&utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=beginner-s-guide-to-licensing-your-mods",195,[50,93,292],[268,307],[377],[30740,30741,30742],"W1ls1Zlr","aqt1jSWW","wGy9b99l","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3lVgdjw/3d34aa2a10ea4bad8e19e094f8c73437b12cb620_96.webp","https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Warcraft",[],[30747],{"url":30748,"raw_url":30749,"featured":439,"title":30750,"description":30751,"created":30752,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3lVgdjw/images/b8aca7301b05e691454856076db3a4197df75fd2_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3lVgdjw/images/b8aca7301b05e691454856076db3a4197df75fd2.jpeg","Love","...","2024-10-20T02:35:24.305171Z",2634254,"lbkaJPmH",{"client_side":30037,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":30756,"id":30757,"slug":30758,"project_type":31,"team":30759,"organization":30760,"title":30761,"description":30762,"body":30763,"body_url":3592,"published":30764,"updated":30765,"approved":30766,"queued":30767,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":30768,"downloads":30769,"followers":30265,"categories":30770,"additional_categories":30771,"loaders":30772,"versions":30773,"icon_url":30788,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":30789,"donation_urls":30790,"gallery":30791,"color":30792,"thread_id":30793,"monetization_status":30002},[1049,1043,1010,968,962,890,884,847,841,793,790,760,712,670,661,655,610,604,559,505,499,487,436],"T32YfFqA","treeminer","GkOzw5aH","uS6BlVMT","TreeMiner","A plugin which mines the whole tree for you with geyserMC support","![TreeMiner Description](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/792530045e90eff28754b6ea03d966372cc811c3.png)\n\n\u003Ctable align=\"center\">\n  \u003Ctr>\n    \u003Ctd align=\"center\">\u003Cstrong>Advertisement:\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\n  \u003C/tr>\n\u003C/table>\n\n\u003Cp align=\"center\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0050916bdb29019d91424d8d4b0d59379051c9bf_0.webp\">\n    \u003Cimg src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0050916bdb29019d91424d8d4b0d59379051c9bf_0.webp\" alt=\"Sponsored #1\">\n  \u003C/a>\n\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp align=\"center\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/%E2%9C%A8%E2%98%85-playerconsole-%E2%98%85-folia-%E2%8E%AE-image-motds-%E2%8E%AE-auto-restart-velocity-file-db-managing-api.126241/\">\n    \u003Cimg src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/066fb24e130162857c967c2bdd362481822f9a38.png\" alt=\"Sponsored\">\n  \u003C/a>\n\u003C/p>\n\n\u003Cdetails>\n\u003Csummary>text version\u003C/summary>\n\nTreeMiner Plugin: Enhanced Woodcutting Experience\nTreeMiner is an intuitive and performance-optimized Minecraft plugin that transforms the way players gather wood. With a single swing of your axe, you can fell an entire tree in one swift motion, eliminating the tedious process of chopping each log individually.\nKey Features:\nConnected Log Detection - Automatically identifies and harvests all logs connected to the initially broken block, regardless of wood type (oak, spruce, acacia, etc.)\nSmart Configuration Options:  Toggle sneak requirement for activation\nTool type restrictions (axe only mode)\nPermission-based access control\nConfigurable maximum log count to prevent server lag\n Balanced Gameplay:\nOptional tool durability consumption based on logs harvested\nPreserves vanilla drop rates and enchantment effects\nCompatible with other economy and crafting plugins\nUser-Friendly Commands:\nSimple /treeminer or /tm toggle command\nPersonal preference settings that persist between sessions\n Server Performance Optimized:\nEfficient breadth-first search algorithm for log detection\nMinimal impact on server TPS\nAsynchronous block breaking for smooth gameplay\nWhy Choose This Plugin? This wood harvesting solution strikes the perfect balance between convenience and gameplay integrity. It respects Minecraft's core mechanics while eliminating repetitive tasks that can lead to player fatigue and wrist strain.\nServer administrators will appreciate the lightweight implementation and extensive configuration options, while players will enjoy the seamless integration that feels like a natural extension of vanilla gameplay rather than a game-changing modification.\nWhether you're building a survival server focused on construction or simply want to enhance the quality of life for your players, TreeMiner provides an elegant solution to a common gameplay friction point without compromising the core woodcutting experience.\n\n\u003C/details>\n\n","2025-04-21T14:26:02.700745Z","2026-06-16T15:51:59.595043Z","2025-04-22T21:29:17.786218Z","2025-04-21T14:28:57.872502Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},28391,[30,134,303],[],[329,401,405,417],[30774,30775,30776,30777,30778,30779,30780,30781,30782,30783,30784,30785,30786,30787],"T1cZmDxR","58sPJTWY","golCv56R","U2szKt0f","1axIh6lm","d8lChVOD","o7tfZaDT","hompfmFi","bdexxk0H","Yb8HPft5","i2Q2f7O1","L1XK8p1I","NYR0JuXG","nBNXRn3r","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T32YfFqA/db3426f69084aeff6d3a2e6dac5c4aff23ee69f0_96.webp","https://discord.gg/jFvq2fdUXB",[],[],10046753,"7P3dmIc0",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":30795,"id":30796,"slug":30797,"project_type":31,"team":30798,"organization":3592,"title":30799,"description":30800,"body":30801,"body_url":3592,"published":30802,"updated":30803,"approved":30804,"queued":30805,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":30806,"downloads":30809,"followers":30075,"categories":30810,"additional_categories":30811,"loaders":30812,"versions":30813,"icon_url":30815,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":30816,"gallery":30817,"color":30824,"thread_id":30825,"monetization_status":30002},[655],"T2uyJ0sP","tiers+","wjgKe4fZ","Tiers+","This mod expands the game by introducing additional tiers, offering new levels of progression, challenges, and rewards for players to unlock.","This mod adds an brand new tier packed with fresh challenges, and a whole new level of fun. More tiers are coming soon, so jump in now and be among the first to experience it!\n\n## **Current Tiers**\n1. Serpentium, Ranked Over Diamond.\n2. (Coming Soon) Titanium, Ranked Under Diamond.\n\n## **Ore Generation**\n1. Serpentium: Spawns From -10 To -64.\n2. (Coming Soon) Titanium: Spawns From 20 To -5.\n\nExpect an update that adds a new tier almost every week.","2025-12-23T18:08:29.529006Z","2025-12-24T10:29:03.438321Z","2026-01-06T17:55:03.154998Z","2025-12-24T10:30:46.369453Z",{"id":30807,"name":30808,"url":3592},"CC-BY-NC-ND-4.0","Creative Commons Attribution Non Commercial No Derivatives 4.0 International",28,[30,115,316],[],[385],[30814],"JPSIihIW","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2uyJ0sP/5966865cf4cf2ed43fe4c0d2665d3b9a1f210a00_96.webp",[],[30818],{"url":30819,"raw_url":30820,"featured":439,"title":30821,"description":30822,"created":30823,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2uyJ0sP/images/aeca5051286d68eff7cca115e8d93799a0140870_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2uyJ0sP/images/aeca5051286d68eff7cca115e8d93799a0140870.png","Serpentium","A tier that ranks over diamond.","2025-12-24T10:41:54.492479Z",6025979,"dqayfGbY",{"client_side":30037,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":30827,"id":30828,"slug":30829,"project_type":31,"team":30830,"organization":3592,"title":30831,"description":30832,"body":30833,"body_url":3592,"published":30834,"updated":30835,"approved":30836,"queued":30837,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":30838,"downloads":30399,"followers":29981,"categories":30839,"additional_categories":30840,"loaders":30841,"versions":30842,"icon_url":30845,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":30846,"gallery":30847,"color":30848,"thread_id":30849,"monetization_status":30002},[847,841,793,790,760,712,670,661,655,610,604,559],"T4GrGIGJ","sr-smartchest","RuoVEvxZ","SR SmartChest","A lightweight and efficient smart chest management utility for Minecraft servers.","\u003Ciframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/u1kBdEH7e9Y\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen>\u003C/iframe>\nSR_SmartChest is a lightweight plugin designed to help players manage their chests with greater convenience and speed. Developed with a focus on performance and ease of use, it is suitable for any server type, including Survival, Skyblock, or Community-based environments.  \nHow to Use\nEnable the Feature: Use the command /smartchest on to activate the system.  \nCategorize Your Items: Place one sample item that you wish to categorize into the chest and close it.  \nAutomatic Sorting: Once set, the chest will automatically \"suck\" or pull that specific item type from your inventory.  \nProximity Collection: By simply standing near your categorized chest, it will automatically pull the designated items from your inventory into the chest.  \nFeatures\nLightweight Performance: Built to ensure a smooth experience without taxing server resources.  \nAdvanced Configuration: Additional settings and fine-tuning are available within the config.yml file.  \nSmart Interaction: Uses a dedicated listener system to handle player and chest interactions seamlessly.  \n","2026-05-05T19:49:15.594006Z","2026-05-31T02:32:08.903185Z","2026-05-08T04:06:10.283803Z","2026-05-05T20:03:37.207911Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},[303],[],[329,401,405,417],[30843,30844],"KLmiqcgm","AxG0pRT6","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4GrGIGJ/85ca431e6dcb3819a927a5e65908e80e06698972_96.webp",[],[],13158600,"Yur6VGSP",{"client_side":29949,"server_side":29949,"game_versions":30851,"id":30852,"slug":30853,"project_type":34,"team":30854,"organization":3592,"title":30855,"description":30856,"body":30857,"body_url":3592,"published":30858,"updated":30859,"approved":30860,"queued":30861,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":30862,"downloads":30863,"followers":29981,"categories":30864,"additional_categories":30865,"loaders":30866,"versions":30867,"icon_url":30872,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":30873,"gallery":30878,"color":30884,"thread_id":30885,"monetization_status":30002},[760,712],"T3kZYaup","some-square-optimized-modpack-enthusiasm","2P1hL48t","[SOME] Square Optimized Modpack Enthusiasm","|Its very optimized modpack!|Created by dimonlaktikxD|","_Hi!_ I made a pretty optimized modpack.**There is not A SINGLE mod in it that is NOT related to optimization**.If you have any questions, please contact discord!\nSquare Optimized Modpack Enthusiasm allows you to boost your FPS in minecraft!It's a pretty good modpack that's willing to do a lot to please you .It will help you a lot because there are a lot of optimizing mods!","2025-02-19T21:17:24.455560Z","2025-03-30T18:20:24.309622Z","2025-03-27T21:18:04.322492Z","2025-03-25T19:14:39.426649Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},141,[211],[],[346],[30868,30869,30870,30871],"cPSsYtj5","80IdBIUT","LfE486CK","HCzaPW2L","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3kZYaup/835bb04e4f5c409c51a2d2047271c67fa28093ba_96.webp",[30874,30876],{"id":3152,"platform":3153,"url":30875},"https://www.donationalerts.com/r/dimalaki",{"id":3137,"platform":3138,"url":30877},"https://patreon.com/dim0nl4ktik",[30879],{"url":30880,"raw_url":30881,"featured":439,"title":30882,"description":3592,"created":30883,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3kZYaup/images/5649ac06847ee9ce5005b3d49ccfa8f27ecf0a5b_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3kZYaup/images/5649ac06847ee9ce5005b3d49ccfa8f27ecf0a5b.png","Square Optimized Modpack Enthusiasm","2025-03-23T07:30:24.534361Z",12369084,"krXyWLco",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":30887,"id":30888,"slug":30889,"project_type":31,"team":30890,"organization":30891,"title":30892,"description":30893,"body":30894,"body_url":3592,"published":30895,"updated":30896,"approved":30897,"queued":30898,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":30899,"downloads":30902,"followers":30903,"categories":30904,"additional_categories":30905,"loaders":30906,"versions":30907,"icon_url":30959,"issues_url":30960,"source_url":30961,"wiki_url":30962,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":30963,"gallery":30964,"color":30965,"thread_id":30966,"monetization_status":30002},[1508,1502,1490,1469,1298,1271,1172,1043,847,841],"T38eAZQC","kubejs-create","p2d14DeK","JpMJI35A","KubeJS Create","KubeJS Create integration","[Create](https://modrinth.com/mod/create) integration for [KubeJS](https://modrinth.com/mod/kubejs). This mod allows you to add and properly edit recipes of Create mod in KubeJS scripts. All supported recipe types and examples are below. See [Recipes page](https://mods.latvian.dev/books/kubejs/page/recipeeventjs) for more info.\n\nSupported recipe types:\n\n- `createCrushing`\n- `createCutting`\n- `createMilling`\n- `createBasin`\n- `createMixing` (supports **.heated()** and **.superheated()**)\n- `createCompacting` (supports **.heated()** and **.superheated()**)\n- `createPressing`\n- `createSandpaperPolishing`\n- `createSplashing` (Bulk Washing)\n- `createDeploying`\n- `createFilling`\n- `createEmptying`\n\n> Note: Bulk Smoking = vanilla smoking and Bulk Blasting = vanilla blasting recipe types.\n\n`event.recipes.createCrushing(output[], input[])`\nOutput doesn't have to be an array. It can be either items or fluids\nInput doesn't have to be an array. It can be either ingredients or `Fluid.of('minecraft:water', 1000)` or `{fluidTag: 'some:fluid_tag', amount: 1000}`\n\n### `createMechanicalCrafting`\n\n`event.recipes.createMechanicalCrafting(output, pattern[], {patternKey: input})`\n\nThis recipe type is the same as regular crafting table shaped recipe\n\n```javascript\nevent.recipes.createSequencedAssembly(output[], input, sequence[]) \n// output[] are your output items\n// input is your input item\n// sequence[] is an array of sequences. These sequences are \"regular\" recipes that are supported.\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```javascript\nevent.recipes.createCrushing([\n  '2x minecraft:cobblestone',\n  'minecraft:redstone',\n  Item.of('minecraft:redstone').withChance(0.5)\n], 'minecraft:redstone_ore')\n```\n\n```javascript\nevent.recipes.createMixing('create:chromatic_compound', [\n  '#forge:dusts/glowstone',\n  '#forge:dusts/glowstone',\n  '#forge:dusts/glowstone',\n  'create:powdered_obsidian',\n  'create:powdered_obsidian',\n  'create:powdered_obsidian',\n  'create:polished_rose_quartz'\n]).superheated()\n```\n\n```javascript\nevent.recipes.createFilling('create:blaze_cake', [\n  'create:blaze_cake_base',\n  Fluid.of('minecraft:lava', 250)\n])\n```\n\n```javascript\nevent.recipes.createEmptying([\n  'minecraft:glass_bottle',\n  Fluid.of('create:honey', 250)\n], 'minecraft:honey_bottle')\n```\n\n```javascript\nevent.recipes.createMechanicalCrafting('minecraft:piston', [\n  'CCCCC',\n  'CPIPC',\n  'CPRPC'\n], {\n  C: '#forge:cobblestone',\n  P: '#minecraft:planks',\n  R: '#forge:dusts/redstone',\n  I: '#forge:ingots/iron'\n})\n```\n\n```javascript\nevent.recipes.createSequencedAssembly([ // start the recipe\n Item.of('6x create:large_cogwheel').withChance(32.0), // have this item be an output with a certain chance\n Item.of('create:brass_ingot').withChance(2.0), // have this item be an output with a certain chance\n 'minecraft:andesite', // have this item be a guaranteed output\n 'create:cogwheel', // have this item be a guaranteed output\n 'minecraft:stick', // have this item be a guaranteed output\n 'minecraft:iron_nugget' // have this item be a guaranteed output\n], 'create:brass_ingot', [ // 'create:brass_ingot' is the input.\n// the transitional item set by \"transitionalItem('create:incomplete_large_cogwheel')\" is the item that will be used during the recipe as the item that the input is using to transition to the output.\n event.recipes.createDeploying('create:incomplete_large_cogwheel', ['create:incomplete_large_cogwheel', '#minecraft:planks']), // like a normal recipe function, is used as a sequence step in this array. Input and output have the transitional item\n event.recipes.createDeploying('create:incomplete_large_cogwheel', ['create:incomplete_large_cogwheel', '#minecraft:wooden_buttons']), // like a normal recipe function, is used as a sequence step in this array. Input and output have the transitional item\n event.recipes.createCutting('create:incomplete_large_cogwheel', 'create:incomplete_large_cogwheel').processingTime(50) // like a normal recipe function, is used as a sequence step in this array. Input and output have the transitional item\n]).transitionalItem('create:incomplete_large_cogwheel').loops(6) // set the transitional item and the loops (amount of repetitions)\n```\n\nIf you want to use your own transitional item in sequenced_assembly recipes, you must register it in startup event:\n\n```javascript\nonEvent('item.registry', event => {\n  // Texture for this item goes in kubejs/assets/kubejs/textures/item/my_part.png\n  event.create('my_part', 'create:sequenced_assembly').displayName('My Part')\n})\n```\n\nThen you would use ...`transitionalItem('kubejs:my_part')`...\n\n> Note! Mysterious Conversion recipes are client side only, so the only way to add them currently is using reflection with this code in client scripts (outside any event):\n\n```javascript\nlet MysteriousItemConversionCategory = java('com.simibubi.create.compat.jei.category.MysteriousItemConversionCategory')\nlet ConversionRecipe = java('com.simibubi.create.compat.jei.ConversionRecipe')\n\nMysteriousItemConversionCategory.RECIPES.add(ConversionRecipe.create('minecraft:apple', 'minecraft:carrot'))\nMysteriousItemConversionCategory.RECIPES.add(ConversionRecipe.create('minecraft:golden_apple', 'minecraft:golden_carrot'))\n```\n\n[![](https://links.latvian.dev/links.png?mr=kubejscreate)](https://links.latvian.dev/)\n\n[![](https://links.latvian.dev/partner.png)](https://links.latvian.dev/partner)","2023-08-21T20:20:41.279415Z","2025-11-12T09:22:05.119602Z","2023-08-21T23:33:40.220478Z","2023-08-21T22:24:05.778206Z",{"id":30900,"name":30901,"url":3592},"LGPL-3.0-only","GNU Lesser General Public License v3.0 only",1445536,84,[303],[157],[346,354,385],[30908,30909,30910,30911,30912,30913,30914,30915,30916,30917,30918,30919,30920,30921,30922,30923,30924,30925,30926,30927,30928,30929,30930,30931,30932,30933,30934,30935,30936,30937,30938,30939,30940,30941,30942,30943,30944,30945,30946,30947,30948,30949,30950,30951,30952,30953,30954,30955,30956,30957,30958],"MO75e2sC","YN0T5Pmf","dvLO7wuv","T4V6Dm0l","cNEVOQ4q","bnvthbJW","uMNhEyBG","79c3Pl6W","VwLRcUBQ","Khlo8swW","b3ZbuHEY","eRR2DuIi","CDoBzOhr","qmHwp7h4","gUgBKKro","r6cVLbDS","I3cYQ3mX","pLyqKVXT","ftDL2MOo","XABryG8V","VszJSnhB","1INYEb9w","oRValdcl","mHfUZDSO","m9lk8iMr","65oHVwN8","VLiijTOY","rJ26X7G5","2Hq8tbrn","dxY7VzQv","zWLaf3WR","Yp60zntL","B4zWSIIO","8qUQlsto","zmzcrZEp","y7FC6Rsp","YE9yQwxx","353BVKVV","hYdnSDQB","13yE1QX6","Jqn5DRIj","A0KQFxde","Xe2y2pRp","FhVbUfLB","ClnUsQ85","HJ0xIlkM","PB33MOc1","hei9cDRa","y2WfxPp9","5vppyenb","1qmcLagN","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T38eAZQC/a64dad7d028d11258640b48798614759ae1fb2a4_96.webp","https://kubejs.com/support?source=kubejs_create","https://github.com/KubeJS-Mods/KubeJS-Create","https://kubejs.com/",[],[],2429498,"Zc00fS19",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":30968,"id":30969,"slug":30970,"project_type":31,"team":30971,"organization":3592,"title":30972,"description":30973,"body":30974,"body_url":3592,"published":30975,"updated":30976,"approved":30977,"queued":30978,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":30979,"downloads":30980,"followers":30404,"categories":30981,"additional_categories":30982,"loaders":30983,"versions":30984,"icon_url":30986,"issues_url":30987,"source_url":30988,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":30989,"gallery":30990,"color":31057,"thread_id":31058,"monetization_status":30002},[841],"T3bLJPwA","new-world-of-color","XZEMEFSm","New World Of Color","Adds 16 new dye colors (and all associated blocks) to expand the vanilla color palette!","\nAbout New World Of Color\n=======\n\nThis mod adds 16 new dye colors to the game! Dyes ~~are~~ _will be_ compatible with all vanilla use cases and make an effort to be as vanilla-friendly as possible. All recipes should unlock in the recipe book when you collect the needed ingredients.\n\n**THIS MOD IS CURRENTLY IN BETA! The following features are missing for the new colors at the moment:**\n* Banners\n* Dying leather/wolf armor\n* Dying pet collars\n* Fireworks\n* Llama carpets\n\nAdditionally, these are known parity issues that may or may not get resolved:\n* Villagers will not recognize beds that are dyed with a new color as a valid home\n* Text on signs CAN be dyed using the new dyes, but it will apply the closest available vanilla color instead of one perfectly matching the dye used\n\nMod Compatability\n--------------------------\nDyed items from other mods will naturally not be able to use the new colors until/unless support is added, but otherwise this mod should _generally_ be compatible with other mods! However, there is one possible concern with the way **sheep** are handled. This mod will replace all sheep with a modded duplicate that supports the new colors, so if another mod modifies sheep or relies specifically on vanilla sheep for something it may cause issues.\n\nAdditionally, the stained glass from this mod has built in support for this colored lighting mod!: [https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/colorful-lighting/files/6948201](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/colorful-lighting/files/6948201)\n\nDye Colors And Sources:\n--------------------------\n(All dyes can also be crafted using all of the basic dyes that make up their main color components, \nex. Teal is Cyan+Green but can also be made with Blue+Green+Green)\n* **Crimson** -- Darker shade of red\n  * Red + Black\n  * Crafting Crimson Roots gives 1 dye\n* **Vermilion** -- Red-Orange\n  * Red + Orange\n* **Amber** -- Yellow-Orange\n  * Orange + Yellow\n  * Smelting Honeycomb gives 1 dye\n* **Chartreuse** -- Yellow-Green\n  * Lime + Yellow\n* **Olive** -- Lighter shade of vanilla green\n  * Green + White\n* **Spring Green** -- Brighter, more vibrant shade of green than the vanilla dye\n  * Green + Green\n* **Jade** -- Vibrant dark green\n  * Spring Green + Black\n* **Teal** -- Blue-Green\n  * Cyan + Green\n  * Crafting Warped Roots gives 1 dye\n* **Turquoise** -- Lighter Blue-Green\n  * Cyan + White\n* **Azure** -- Medium Blue\n  * Blue + White\n  * Crafting Azure Bluets gives 1 dye\n* **Indigo** -- Darker, more blue shade of purple\n  * Purple + Blue\n* **Mauve** -- Light Purple\n  * Purple + White\n  * Crafting Chorus Fruit gives 1 dye\n* **Fuchsia** -- Dark Magenta\n  * Purple + Crimson\n  * Crafting Spore Blossoms gives 4 dye\n* **Coral** -- Dark, somewhat orangey pink\n  * Orange + Pink\n  * Smelting Brain Coral (Normal or fans, not blocks) gives 1 dye\n* **Burgundy** -- Dark, reddish purple. You might also know the color as \"wine\" or \"maroon\"\n  * Crafting Torchflowers gives 4 dye\n  * (Cannot by made by mixing colors)\n* **Light Brown** -- Light Brown\n  * Brown + White\n\nVanilla Tweaks:\n--------------------------\nThe mod makes a very small number of tweaks to vanilla recipes/textures(All of which can be easily undone/overrided with a resource pack if needed):\n* Lime Dye had its recipe changed to not overlap with Olive, which had no other logical recipe\n  * Lime Dye is now made with: Green + Yellow dye\n* Light Blue dye had its recipe changed to make room for Azure as a step between it and normal blue\n  * Light Blue Dye is now made with: Azure + White dye\n* The Azure Bluet texture was updated to give the flowers a noticeable blue color(without straying too far from vanilla, it's still subtle), and they now craft into Azure dye instead of Light Gray\n  * (The real life flowers are in fact most often blue, hence azure being in the name, so I honestly don't know why they didn't already reflect that and give light blue dye in vanilla)\n* The Torchflower texture was updated to further emphasize the reddish-purple elements to make the burgundy dye connection clearer","2025-09-07T00:25:52.740598Z","2025-09-07T01:23:46.336255Z","2025-09-08T03:44:12.639185Z","2025-09-08T03:22:19.097415Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},558,[100],[],[385],[30985],"nNiqEo52","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/66f2c859909f37f82b0c6b0898bfef77d05c4d64.png","https://github.com/AvengingCondor/NewWorldOfColor/issues","https://github.com/AvengingCondor/NewWorldOfColor",[],[30991,30997,31003,31008,31014,31019,31025,31030,31036,31042,31047,31052],{"url":30992,"raw_url":30993,"featured":439,"title":30994,"description":3592,"created":30995,"ordering":30996},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/b7d776e210ad086a10faf19deb60afae9727ada9_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/b7d776e210ad086a10faf19deb60afae9727ada9.png","All Dyed Blocks and Features","2025-09-07T03:03:15.927050Z",-2,{"url":30998,"raw_url":30999,"featured":439,"title":31000,"description":3592,"created":31001,"ordering":31002},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/81d20debcef98d82309c27c383b87824ad5a5800_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/81d20debcef98d82309c27c383b87824ad5a5800.png","Glazed Terracotta Patterns","2025-09-07T03:07:30.829708Z",-1,{"url":31004,"raw_url":31005,"featured":439,"title":31006,"description":3592,"created":31007,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/4c6a02316c46cae91e3b199ceb5b4533d845864d_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/4c6a02316c46cae91e3b199ceb5b4533d845864d.png","Gradients","2025-09-07T03:06:36.234142Z",{"url":31009,"raw_url":31010,"featured":849,"title":31011,"description":31012,"created":31013,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/957237f0e375d99f0099619bb56a05f3d7bd47fe_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/957237f0e375d99f0099619bb56a05f3d7bd47fe.png","Full Spectrum","Colors marked on top are new, bottom are vanilla","2025-09-07T03:05:55.202906Z",{"url":31015,"raw_url":31016,"featured":439,"title":31017,"description":3592,"created":31018,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/a32f99943574c57fef87934799e9e465639356da_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/a32f99943574c57fef87934799e9e465639356da.png","Color Palette","2025-09-07T03:06:24.643765Z",{"url":31020,"raw_url":31021,"featured":439,"title":31022,"description":31023,"created":31024,"ordering":29981},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/138d3eb3a4adbcaf98367fa10d46a990cdf44230_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/138d3eb3a4adbcaf98367fa10d46a990cdf44230.png","Sample Build","Using several different blocks from the mod for decoration","2025-09-07T03:12:03.618194Z",{"url":31026,"raw_url":31027,"featured":439,"title":31028,"description":3592,"created":31029,"ordering":29981},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/47b8c2bb60bc238e925586ffc3a0a87aa38170f0_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/47b8c2bb60bc238e925586ffc3a0a87aa38170f0.png","More Sample Gradients/Applications","2025-09-07T03:12:48.397449Z",{"url":31031,"raw_url":31032,"featured":439,"title":31033,"description":31034,"created":31035,"ordering":29981},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/6c937f54b1335d47320c38cbcea392480edad97f_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/6c937f54b1335d47320c38cbcea392480edad97f.png","Skulk Room","Using Turquoise Glazed Terracotta for the floor!","2025-09-07T03:11:06.104758Z",{"url":31037,"raw_url":31038,"featured":439,"title":31039,"description":31040,"created":31041,"ordering":29981},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/7d2eab827584ad9a35cb32de41b64b35bf6fd4fe_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/7d2eab827584ad9a35cb32de41b64b35bf6fd4fe.png","Tweaked Flower Textures","Torchflowers had their reddish-purple elements tweaked and emphasized to make the burgundy dye connection clearer, Azure Bluets were given a hint of blue on the flowers so that they can rightly give Azure dye","2025-09-07T03:05:07.676767Z",{"url":31043,"raw_url":31044,"featured":439,"title":31045,"description":3592,"created":31046,"ordering":29987},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/5b6e3b943f007c7156e83f4b8b3ac303a7cbf6d7_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/5b6e3b943f007c7156e83f4b8b3ac303a7cbf6d7.png","Smelting For Amber Dye","2025-09-07T03:08:45.093304Z",{"url":31048,"raw_url":31049,"featured":439,"title":31050,"description":3592,"created":31051,"ordering":29987},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/6c574fe144613571ccf3113ee3ca2c763e1607cc_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/6c574fe144613571ccf3113ee3ca2c763e1607cc.png","Crafting Teal Dye","2025-09-07T03:08:57.771911Z",{"url":31053,"raw_url":31054,"featured":439,"title":31055,"description":3592,"created":31056,"ordering":29987},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/9db8cc7293b4014f74fab82dae114b3fcc205395_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3bLJPwA/images/9db8cc7293b4014f74fab82dae114b3fcc205395.png","Dye Items","2025-09-07T03:09:12.913347Z",4236312,"gIhtfjti",{"client_side":30037,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31060,"id":31061,"slug":31062,"project_type":31,"team":31063,"organization":3592,"title":31064,"description":31065,"body":31066,"body_url":3592,"published":31067,"updated":31068,"approved":31067,"queued":3592,"status":29937,"requested_status":3592,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31069,"downloads":31070,"followers":31071,"categories":31072,"additional_categories":31073,"loaders":31074,"versions":31075,"icon_url":31086,"issues_url":31087,"source_url":31088,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":31089,"gallery":31092,"color":31093,"thread_id":31061,"monetization_status":30002},[1271,1214,1208,1205,1202,1199,1196,1193,1190,1187,1184,1181,1172,1136,1097,1049,1043,1010,968,962,890,884,847,841,793,790,760],"T4Cv5iZq","opac-fabric-create-support","nf8TfL49","(Legacy) Create Support for Open Parties and Claims","Adds Fabric Create mod support to Open Parties and Claims","_**This extension requires Create 0.5.1.f or newer since version 1.6.0 of the extension!**_\n\n1.3.0 - 1.5.0 requires Create 0.5.1.b - 0.5.1.d!\n\n1.1.0 - 1.2.0 only works with Create v0.5.0!\n\n1.0.0 only works with Create v0.4.1 Patch 13 or older!\n\nThis Fabric mod adds [Create](https://modrinth.com/mod/create-fabric) mod support to chunk protection in the [Open Parties and Claims](https://modrinth.com/mod/open-parties-and-claims) mod.\n\nReleased separately from the main mod to avoid crashes in the development environment and errors in the logs in any environment when Create isn't present. The Forge version of OPAC supports Create by default and you don't need this extension.","2022-07-26T13:12:44.086993Z","2025-02-27T10:05:58.312388Z",{"id":30900,"name":30901,"url":3592},1318201,94,[303],[],[346,409],[31076,31077,31078,31079,31080,31081,31082,31083,31084,31085],"UcbJd9sQ","JnCTHLbn","Ho1YNNQK","wmC1kRNL","UmKySKmr","BFyubP9L","gtBSrlaf","Cf65NVxT","8Qykx4mx","7PmrMoon","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4Cv5iZq/icon.png","https://github.com/thexaero/open-parties-and-claims/issues","https://github.com/thexaero/opac-fabric-create-support",[31090],{"id":3137,"platform":3138,"url":31091},"https://www.patreon.com/xaero96",[],8707324,{"client_side":30037,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31095,"id":31096,"slug":31097,"project_type":31,"team":31098,"organization":3592,"title":31099,"description":31100,"body":31101,"body_url":3592,"published":31102,"updated":31103,"approved":31104,"queued":31105,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31106,"downloads":31107,"followers":30075,"categories":31108,"additional_categories":31109,"loaders":31110,"versions":31111,"icon_url":31113,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":31114,"donation_urls":31115,"gallery":31116,"color":31117,"thread_id":31118,"monetization_status":30002},[2942,2939,2936,2933,2930,1049,1043,1010,968,962,890,884,847,841,793,790,760,712,670,661,655,610,604,559],"T3FDK4uq","veinminer-plus","56Lg9iHg","VeinminerPlus","Ability to mine whole veins at once","# VeinminerPlus\n\nVeinminerPlus is a highly customizable vein mining plugin for Paper and Spigot servers (1.20+). Break entire ore veins and tree logs with a single block break while respecting tool requirements and durability. Every setting can be adjusted per player group, per vein type, and even per individual block.\n\n## Features\n\n- **Vein mine ores and logs** – Break connected blocks of the same type instantly or with a configurable delay.\n- **Fully configurable blocks and tools** – Define which blocks can be vein mined and exactly which tools are required.\n- **Player groups with granular control** – Create groups like `vip` and `premium` with custom limits, activation modes, and break speeds.\n- **Per-vein and per-block overrides** – Set different max blocks, distances, and settings for specific ores or logs within the same group.\n- **Multiple activation modes** – Choose between `NONE` (always active) or `SNEAK` (crouch to activate).\n- **Tool damage and Unbreaking support** – Optionally apply durability loss for extra blocks broken, with full respect for the Unbreaking enchantment.\n- **Instant or delayed breaking** – Break all blocks at once or sequentially with a tick delay to prevent server lag.\n- **Admin commands with tab completion** – Toggle vein mining globally, per player, or per group. Reload configuration on the fly.\n- **Permission-based groups** – Players join groups via permissions like `veinminerplus.group.vip` (no extra YAML files required).\n\n## Commands\n\n| Command | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| `/veinminer reload` | Reload the configuration from disk. |\n| `/veinminer toggle global \u003Con\\|off>` | Enable or disable vein mining for everyone. |\n| `/veinminer toggle player \u003Cname> \u003Con\\|off>` | Toggle vein mining for a specific player. |\n| `/veinminer toggle group \u003Cgroup> \u003Con\\|off>` | Enable or disable an entire player group. |\n| `/veinminer status [player]` | Show global, group, and per-player status. |\n| `/veinminer set global activation \u003CNONE\\|SNEAK>` | Change the global activation mode. |\n| `/veinminer set group \u003Cgroup> activation \u003CNONE\\|SNEAK>` | Change a group's activation mode. |\n\nAll commands have full tab completion for arguments.\n\n## Permissions\n\n| Permission | Description |\n|------------|-------------|\n| `veinminerplus.admin` | Access to all admin commands. |\n| `veinminerplus.use` | Allows vein mining (subject to toggles). |\n| `veinminerplus.group.vip` | Membership in the VIP group. |\n| `veinminerplus.group.premium` | Membership in the Premium group. |\n\n## Installation\n\n1. Download the latest `VeinminerPlus-x.x.x.jar`.\n2. Place the JAR file into your server's `plugins` folder.\n3. Restart your server (or run `/reload confirm`).\n4. Edit the generated `config.yml` to your liking.\n5. Use `/veinminer reload` to apply changes without restarting.\n\n## Support\n\nFor issues, feature requests, or questions, please join our [Discord server](https://discord.gg/hrQXF9TfvS).\n---\n\n*VeinminerPlus is built for Paper 1.20+ and requires no additional dependencies.*\n\n## Configuration\n\nThe configuration is divided into intuitive sections. Below is an annotated excerpt showing the main components.\n\n```yaml\n# Global defaults (fallback values)\nglobal-enabled: true\nmax-blocks: 64\nmax-distance: 16\napply-tool-damage: true\napply-unbreaking: true\nactivation-mode: SNEAK\nbreak-mode:\n  instant: true\n  delay-ticks: 1\n\n# Predefined tool sets for easy reference\ndefault-tools:\n  ores-tools: [WOODEN_PICKAXE, STONE_PICKAXE, IRON_PICKAXE, DIAMOND_PICKAXE, NETHERITE_PICKAXE]\n  logs-tools: [WOODEN_AXE, STONE_AXE, IRON_AXE, DIAMOND_AXE, NETHERITE_AXE]\n\n# Vein groups define which blocks belong together and what tools can break them\nvein-groups:\n  low-tier-ores:\n    blocks:\n      COAL_ORE: {}\n      COPPER_ORE: {}\n    tools: ores-tools\n\n  mid-tier-ores:\n    blocks:\n      IRON_ORE: {}\n      GOLD_ORE: {}\n      DIAMOND_ORE:\n        max-blocks: 10      # Per-block override\n    tools: mid-tier-ores-tools\n\n  logs:\n    blocks:\n      OAK_LOG: {}\n      SPRUCE_LOG: {}\n    tools: logs-tools\n\n# Player groups define who can vein mine what, with full override capability\nplayer-groups:\n  default:\n    vein-groups:\n      low-tier-ores:\n        enabled: true\n      logs:\n        enabled: true\n    max-blocks: 64\n    activation-mode: SNEAK\n    break-mode:\n      instant: false\n      delay-ticks: 2\n\n  vip:\n    permission: veinminerplus.group.vip\n    enabled: false\n    vein-groups:\n      low-tier-ores:\n        enabled: true\n        activation-mode: NONE\n      mid-tier-ores:\n        enabled: true\n        max-blocks: 200\n    max-blocks: 128\n    activation-mode: SNEAK\n    break-mode:\n      instant: true","2026-04-17T22:04:18.363136Z","2026-04-19T13:40:23.873855Z","2026-04-29T04:02:43.124822Z","2026-04-19T14:23:18.027699Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},53,[115,175,303],[],[401],[31112],"dW4xTKP5","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3FDK4uq/2bbb30debfa216faccc475402543af0ee9a925d0_96.webp","https://discord.gg/hrQXF9TfvS",[],[],6905422,"SZSoqKjj",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31120,"id":31121,"slug":31122,"project_type":31,"team":31123,"organization":3592,"title":31124,"description":31125,"body":31126,"body_url":3592,"published":31127,"updated":31128,"approved":31129,"queued":31130,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31131,"downloads":31132,"followers":29981,"categories":31133,"additional_categories":31134,"loaders":31135,"versions":31136,"icon_url":31138,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":31139,"gallery":31140,"color":31147,"thread_id":31148,"monetization_status":30002},[841],"T3qkEHcy","minoc-dimension","8Cjg1iN4","Minoc Dimension","A modification of my mod Warden Depths that adds 1 biome inspired by the youtuber Minoc.","# Minoc Meadows\n\nThis new mod expands the **Warden Depths** mod by introducing a brand-new biome and rebalancing certain features to make progression faster.\n\n⚠️ Do not install both this mod and the warden depths one, this mod is a standalone.\n\nThe main addition is the **Minoc Meadow**, a peaceful yet mysterious area inhabited by **four new mobs**:\n\n---\n\n## 🪨 Wyktaur Golem\nInspired by the YouTuber **Wyktaur**, this gentle giant roams the meadows.  \nGive him **watermelon**, and he will occasionally reward you with **emeralds**.  \nHowever, be careful—if you hit him, he won’t hesitate to fight back.\n\n![Wyktaur golem](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/24a19553bc19e2e6c82bad35a1516031a5634ce8.webp)\n\n---\n\n## 🌾 Dart Slime\nBased on the YouTuber **Dart**, this bouncy creature wanders calmly through the fields.  \nDefeating it yields **wheat**, which is particularly useful for completing the **Offering Chest** quest from the Warden Depths mod.\n\n![Dart Slime and Minoc](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c10d48fa7554f01fb24a1b6f5c2191c507a031a7_0.webp)\n\n---\n\n## 🐺 Minoc Wolf\nStronger than a vanilla wolf, the **Minoc Wolf** can be tamed using **Warden Berries**.  \nForm your own powerful pack to help you face the dangers of the biome!\n\n![Minoc Wolf and Minoc, meeting for the first time](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1ccaf86b1a43b4003c7aa35268efa322ba194f54_0.webp)\n\n---\n\n## 💀 Minoc Wither (Boss)\nThe mighty **Minoc Wither** is the boss of this biome and spawns **very rarely** in the meadows.  \nWith **five aggressive heads** that shoot **blue fireballs**, it is a formidable opponent.  \nDefeating it grants you a **Nether Star**, another important item required for the **Offering Chest**.\n\n![The Minoc Wither](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a8eb3c49c00d5a325a5a57de8587c641e49b60e9.png)\n\n\n# The Warden Depths\n\nThe original mod introduces a **brand-new dimension** to Minecraft: the **Warden Depths**.  \nTo access it, you must first obtain a **Warden Key**, dropped by the Warden itself, and bring it to the **giant portal frame** found in Ancient Cities.\n\nOnce inside, you’ll discover **three unique biomes** — the **Frozen Valley**, the **Trials!Forest**, and the **Warden Twilight**.  \nEach biome is tied to a special quest that can be tracked in the **Warden Book**, rewarding you with the mythical items of the Warden once completed.\n\n![Warden book menu](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4517011562f259723c2b47733743f500cb206984.png)\n\n---\n\n## ❄️ The Frozen Valley\n\nA vast frozen wasteland of **snow and ice**, home to two new mobs: the **Yeti** and the **Snow Mole**.\n\n![Yeti and Sow Mole](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/689a39e67e3e2c25816d8113b4e4666f7c2a72db.png)\n\nHere, you can mine a new ore called **Ice Shard**, used to craft **frozen versions** of the chest and dispenser — upgraded variants of the vanilla blocks.  \nYou can also use it to build the **Offering Chest**, an essential part of one of the three Warden Book quests.  \n\n![Offering Chest](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/7e216677e10b7f70315812cada48d9e9b565d57f.png)\n\nThis quest is a **farming challenge**, where you must fill the chest with specific resources to complete your task.\n\n![Offering Chest Menu](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/cf82da539a65b1f9812564daab92b3c47dc96a8f.png)\n\nOnce fulfilled, you’ll earn the right to mine the **Primal Crystal**, which contains the **Warden Multitool** — a powerful artifact capable of breaking any block faster than any other tool.  \n\n![Ice primal Crystal](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/324a25c6cfd72d841a36468b4ccee16967f23be9_0.webp)\n\nIt also allows you to **teleport to Warden Squids** roaming the biome, helping you travel faster across the dimension.\n\n![Replace this with a description](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/05fdd023a76ba8adbf133ada12f977bf3b1ed98a.png)\n\n⚠️ **Beware:** The temperature in this biome is dangerously low!  \nKeep a torch or another heat source in hand to avoid freezing and taking damage.\n\n---\n\n## 🌲 The Trials Forest\n\nIn this mystical, blue forest stands a massive structure: the **Tower of Trials**.  \nEach floor presents a different challenge — **parkour**, **combat**, **puzzles**, and **mazes**.\n\n![Tower of Trials](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/781c42e4bf2d62dbc694ea40c1e4307cbd516a60_0.webp)\n\nYour goal is to climb to the very top, where you’ll obtain the second mythical item: the **Warden Hammer**.\n\nHowever, to break the ore at the summit, you’ll first need to **complete most of Minecraft’s achievements**, making this dimension truly **endgame content**.\n\n  ![Warden Hammer Crystal](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/83556ac593404c5e57cc31f72c8bc793668ed737.png)\n\n---\n\n## 🌌 The Warden Twilight\n\nThe final biome immerses you in total darkness.  \nNavigate through waves of **Warden Blazes** and **Sculk Sensors** to reach the heart of the area — the **Warden Castle**.\n\n![Warden Blazes](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a88b978efc34cffbe7f809095a0b0fe577184474.png)\n\n![Warden Castle](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/d6ab53ecf233f061d987fcb6b8da626ae957bfb9.png)\n\nInside, you’ll find valuable loot, but your true objective lies deeper: defeating the **Mega Warden**, the ruler of the castle.  \nOnce slain, you’ll gain access to the final crystal, which holds the **Warden Dagger** — the last of the mythical items.\n\n![Mega Warden](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e90737b5008bfb36cd5ba2d997e849d626411833.png)\n\nYou’ll also encounter **Warden Berries**, a mysterious fruit that **stuns nearby mobs** when eaten.\n\n![Warden Berries](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/68fd014d709b6e2fe79644cc8632c9ea755137ae.png)\n\n---\n\n> ⚒️ This entire mod was developed in just **one week** as part of a YouTube challenge — so there might still be a few bugs or missing details.  \nThanks for your understanding and support!\n","2025-11-27T07:26:26.955165Z","2025-11-27T13:39:10.875615Z","2025-12-01T04:15:54.984313Z","2025-11-27T13:41:01.436701Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},263,[30,316],[115,131,191],[385],[31137],"cPz9bh30","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3qkEHcy/fd1994024d43761fccc87eba162afe9f6052c6e4_96.webp",[],[31141],{"url":31142,"raw_url":31143,"featured":849,"title":31144,"description":31145,"created":31146,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3qkEHcy/images/24a19553bc19e2e6c82bad35a1516031a5634ce8_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3qkEHcy/images/24a19553bc19e2e6c82bad35a1516031a5634ce8.webp","The Wyjktaur Golem","The wyktaur golem from Minoc Meadows mod.","2025-11-27T13:40:46.192044Z",2311506,"erCoKxe9",{"client_side":29949,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31150,"id":31151,"slug":31152,"project_type":31,"team":31153,"organization":3592,"title":31154,"description":31155,"body":31156,"body_url":3592,"published":31157,"updated":31158,"approved":31159,"queued":31160,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31161,"downloads":31162,"followers":30075,"categories":31163,"additional_categories":31164,"loaders":31165,"versions":31166,"icon_url":31168,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":31169,"gallery":31170,"color":31175,"thread_id":31176,"monetization_status":30002},[1928,1904,1895,1778,1769,1754,1739,1715,1646,1640,1631,1541,1538,1508,1502,1490,1469,1394,1376,1313,1298,1271,1214,1181,1172,1136,1097,1049,1043,1010,968,962],"T3mVEBew","saddle-recipe-data-pack","nWKetBsu","Saddle Recipe Data Pack","Have you ever felt like finding a saddle instead of crafting one is just too annoying?","# Saddle Recipe Data Pack\n\nThis is just a simple recipe data pack, nothing special.\n\n20100625-2; Added saddles. Saddles do not drop from saddled pigs. Saddles can be found in the new dungeon chests.\n\nOn 25 June 2010 when saddles were added to the game they weren't all the different aside from texture and that saddles didn't drop from saddled pigs until 12w36a.\n\n5 leather and 3 iron will get you a saddle. \n- 1 leather, 1 leather, 1 leather\n- 1 leather, 1 iron, 1 leather\n- 1 iron, empty space, 1 iron\n\n**Side Note**: The game will most likely tell you that the data pack is out of data depending on the version you are choosing to play but it works just fine 1.13-1.20\n\n![recipe](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/72c30ffaff59bd57ac0074905f523d1152ba427e.png)","2024-03-29T15:05:27.390037Z","2024-03-29T15:06:42.057689Z","2024-03-31T00:48:05.404577Z","2024-03-29T15:12:37.914203Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},214,[115,134,175],[303],[342],[31167],"fhc6iFUJ","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3mVEBew/72c30ffaff59bd57ac0074905f523d1152ba427e.png",[],[31171],{"url":31172,"raw_url":31172,"featured":439,"title":31173,"description":3592,"created":31174,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3mVEBew/images/72c30ffaff59bd57ac0074905f523d1152ba427e.png","recipe","2024-03-29T15:05:47.877269Z",12895428,"2lqWHNen",{"client_side":29949,"server_side":29949,"game_versions":31178,"id":31179,"slug":31180,"project_type":34,"team":31181,"organization":3592,"title":31182,"description":31183,"body":31184,"body_url":3592,"published":31185,"updated":31186,"approved":31187,"queued":31188,"status":29937,"requested_status":29939,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31189,"downloads":31190,"followers":29987,"categories":31191,"additional_categories":31192,"loaders":31193,"versions":31194,"icon_url":31200,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":31201,"gallery":31202,"color":31208,"thread_id":31209,"monetization_status":30002},[1043],"T36wok74","havencrest","3OFqNv7A","Havencrest","The modpack for a server where you can be anything.","A modpack with all different types of mods for a medieval RPG-style game that stays true (for the most part) to Vanilla Minecraft's aesthetic! You'll find various QoL improvements as well as large mods like Create, Small Ships, Better Combat, and all of the RPG Series mods.","2024-09-21T22:55:26.142956Z","2024-09-26T05:06:34.916592Z","2024-09-23T08:32:46.240788Z","2024-09-22T04:27:54.658439Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},306,[30,77,171],[200,211,288],[346],[31195,31196,31197,31198,31199],"vaJePoD1","xRh6nZr8","Lajl732o","ictZ0Qhs","quHlqAus","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T36wok74/4cfea19aa2a1f16ffd4c1dadb38e286e3960e7e2_96.webp",[],[31203],{"url":31204,"raw_url":31205,"featured":849,"title":31206,"description":3592,"created":31207,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T36wok74/images/83cf2d8e0212c5052c3e3b31d3edf804bcbbd025_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T36wok74/images/83cf2d8e0212c5052c3e3b31d3edf804bcbbd025.png","Havencrest Logo","2024-09-22T04:26:38.397706Z",3221561,"B4wGjOn6",{"client_side":30037,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31211,"id":31212,"slug":31213,"project_type":31,"team":31214,"organization":3592,"title":31215,"description":31216,"body":31217,"body_url":3592,"published":31218,"updated":31219,"approved":31220,"queued":31221,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31222,"downloads":31223,"followers":29987,"categories":31224,"additional_categories":31225,"loaders":31226,"versions":31227,"icon_url":31229,"issues_url":31230,"source_url":31231,"wiki_url":31232,"discord_url":31233,"donation_urls":31234,"gallery":31239,"color":31246,"thread_id":31247,"monetization_status":30002},[1172,1136],"T4Q6Rl4W","satu-morning!","zHrH7uI1","Satu-Morning!","Satu-Morning is a mod that tells you good morning, and your food level in numeral number format for when you wake up!","When you wake up, the mod tells you \"Good Morning\", along with your food level.","2023-09-06T05:28:54.640783Z","2023-09-06T05:34:22.381136Z","2023-09-08T05:08:54.650665Z","2023-09-07T03:34:06.844552Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},162,[134,303],[],[346],[31228],"AEdF6LY0","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4Q6Rl4W/f933f9c67de4b6d313209495bbde434bfc1db58a.png","https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ANrHYp-LoNpfnhCixiLJsSWN7TFb4fBjVKykjzXQFaw/edit?usp=sharing","https://docs.google.com/document/d/1vxfOLDYEbrZGVSrh8yY2SJ0rqUlsXK1aLhhb39wwK-o/edit?usp=sharing","https://docs.google.com/document/d/1aOhCXn8vWfX_L6huEIpfqV1dWoDFidLzt_Iz2p6N9GQ/edit?usp=sharing","https://discord.gg/dNKxs6dS",[31235,31237],{"id":3143,"platform":30113,"url":31236},"https://www.paypal.com/paypalme/EdwardKhrabrov",{"id":3137,"platform":3138,"url":31238},"https://www.patreon.com/McreatorMods/membership",[31240],{"url":31241,"raw_url":31242,"featured":849,"title":31243,"description":31244,"created":31245,"ordering":29981},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4Q6Rl4W/images/3d4c1287a4e731dfd238f8b13fd16e0116be5461_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4Q6Rl4W/images/3d4c1287a4e731dfd238f8b13fd16e0116be5461.png","Getting Out of bed/Waking up message!","When I woke up, it tells me good morning and my food level.","2023-09-06T05:40:56.568926Z",263172,"NhiEVa7o",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31249,"id":31250,"slug":31251,"project_type":31,"team":31252,"organization":3592,"title":31253,"description":31254,"body":31255,"body_url":3592,"published":31256,"updated":31257,"approved":31258,"queued":31259,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31260,"downloads":31261,"followers":29993,"categories":31262,"additional_categories":31263,"loaders":31264,"versions":31265,"icon_url":31267,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":31268,"gallery":31269,"color":31270,"thread_id":31271,"monetization_status":30002},[962],"T2skd5mr","not-enough-enchants","oGfuoCVT","Not Enough Enchants","A mod that adds some QOL and fun enchants!","This mod adds a bit more enchants to Minecraft, whether they're for fun, or for QOL.\n\n# Currently Avaliable Enchants:\n\n**Frost Bolt** - a crossbow enchant that, upon hitting a target, freezes them (like freezing an entity in powdered snow) for 200 ticks/10 seconds, reducing their movement speed and dealing a bit of damage. Cannot be combined with Quick Charge.\n\n**Updraft** - a shovel enchant that, upon hitting a target whilst they're in mid-air, launches them up even further (about 5 blocks). This is pretty useful for combos.","2024-05-28T15:03:16.344635Z","2024-05-28T15:14:41.296938Z","2024-05-29T21:28:30.067869Z","2024-05-28T15:13:02.536966Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},130,[115,134,171],[],[385],[31266],"fqJw3Y6M","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2skd5mr/e4671e3012315b5466c546a75b4afe1d6ca1c3f8.png",[],[],1162723,"nyoOOzAV",{"client_side":29949,"server_side":29949,"game_versions":31273,"id":31274,"slug":31275,"project_type":31,"team":31276,"organization":3592,"title":31277,"description":31278,"body":31279,"body_url":3592,"published":31280,"updated":31281,"approved":31282,"queued":31283,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31284,"downloads":31285,"followers":30265,"categories":31286,"additional_categories":31287,"loaders":31288,"versions":31289,"icon_url":31327,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":31328,"gallery":31329,"color":31330,"thread_id":31331,"monetization_status":30002},[1715,1631,1469,1376,1271,1172,1097,1043,962,884,841,655],"T38CwbmD","hasi.kick","HQzBbVtI","Kick","Kick your Enemies with Default R!","# For all Versions at/after 2.1\n- now chargeable\n- Overlay\n- full customisable trough the config\n\n\n_Kick with Default R._\n \n_If you only press R, you kick normally._\n_If you sneak and release R, you kick up._\n\n\n\u003Cdetails>\n\u003Csummary>Fabric alternative\u003C/summary>\n\nSpartan Kick: \nhttps://modrinth.com/mod/spartan-kick\n\nBy: **ratralfiofanov**\n\u003C/details>","2025-09-27T16:58:08.924577Z","2026-02-10T18:27:34.673856Z","2025-09-27T22:57:44.132662Z","2025-09-27T17:40:38.566912Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},2607,[134,185,297],[30,93],[354,385],[31290,31291,31292,31293,31294,31295,31296,31297,31298,31299,31300,31301,31302,31303,31304,31305,31306,31307,31308,31309,31310,31311,31312,31313,31314,31315,31316,31317,31318,31319,31320,31321,31322,31323,31324,31325,31326],"JtdNXSyf","uw73kBE5","xBw1IcYN","JSd7f0Ph","z3ddD9JQ","osAYYdDl","uCimWe2D","mvtzYX3M","cd3ZMWQC","Z4nWRBfU","97K5ph6i","ucYQXnqw","E2dxW8x2","qsrE5AAW","NuRFw53h","CJLHJMBY","MjIWUo0U","3ZqG2tV0","cUKGQdGn","ZTQeTMko","pvLvSlFm","Q0d6SSZw","1myfEFny","ogWDmI5W","gmE6E8Bz","a2JwPlAP","kcgzNd6M","9wOa8blc","gOsO6fyd","6dfaw2Mm","RyjUhfEO","UnHPNe9o","7QuHy3Uq","IDtwTmgH","GdgtVMt5","VCjN8kWX","Sqlu8jFK","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T38CwbmD/766f1281bceb21b14e6f952b1f4d845bff36abd7.png",[],[],2171169,"z9EwJOvX",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31333,"id":31334,"slug":31335,"project_type":31,"team":31336,"organization":3592,"title":31337,"description":31338,"body":31339,"body_url":3592,"published":31340,"updated":31341,"approved":31342,"queued":31343,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31344,"downloads":31347,"followers":30399,"categories":31348,"additional_categories":31349,"loaders":31350,"versions":31351,"icon_url":31369,"issues_url":31370,"source_url":31371,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":31372,"gallery":31375,"color":31381,"thread_id":31382,"monetization_status":30002},[1043,962,841],"T34cBZKl","extrastorage","FbFUgXB0","ExtraStorage","Add new blocks to Refined Storage, like more advanced crafters","ExtraStorage is an addon for Refined Storage that enhances your automation and storage capabilities.\n\nAdds 4 upgraded Autocrafter tiers, each offering faster crafting speeds and increased pattern capacity.\n\nIntroduces Advanced Importers and Exporters with 18 filter slots (double the standard).\n\nProvides larger storage options for both items and fluids, including high-capacity Storage Disks, Storage Blocks, and Fluid Storage Blocks.","2023-08-23T12:13:50.258164Z","2026-04-18T16:42:51.264080Z","2023-08-30T00:05:05.737779Z","2023-08-23T13:36:16.425107Z",{"id":31345,"name":31346,"url":3592},"AGPL-3.0-only","GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 only",190400,[279,288,297],[],[354,385],[31352,31353,31354,31355,31356,31357,31358,31359,31360,31361,31362,31363,31364,31365,31366,31367,31368],"3r5J5xaO","i2olWA1r","QacLGbfW","ud9FPTXH","nSoZnKrr","LSn2z31g","olDFbgRO","OYVR7GKa","uUIvo88z","1eTeLB5m","TIwPVmKn","GDceiWAY","Kjjk3fVy","eVFK0lvn","xVf1Pr3H","fAfXhnse","22nfEAlP","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T34cBZKl/5ec950b96e4f8872b22a5944ddd907447e7323ab_96.webp","https://github.com/Edivad99/ExtraStorage/issues","https://github.com/Edivad99/ExtraStorage",[31373],{"id":3143,"platform":30113,"url":31374},"https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted_button_id=RA6ADTD6RE574",[31376],{"url":31377,"raw_url":31378,"featured":849,"title":31379,"description":3592,"created":31380,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T34cBZKl/images/8146ecc60c0657bf2a04465dc4fd2027b2bc99af_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T34cBZKl/images/a0afe07cc19672d3ce35cdd7dc5d2763c3c39cb3.png","Blocks","2023-08-23T12:18:24.752741Z",3355442,"wSvJ0qig",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31384,"id":31385,"slug":31386,"project_type":31,"team":31387,"organization":3592,"title":31388,"description":31389,"body":31390,"body_url":3592,"published":31391,"updated":31392,"approved":31393,"queued":31394,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31395,"downloads":31396,"followers":29993,"categories":31397,"additional_categories":31398,"loaders":31399,"versions":31400,"icon_url":31402,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":31403,"gallery":31404,"color":31429,"thread_id":31430,"monetization_status":30002},[1043],"T42LHFbj","create-pineapples","8nUM3LOE","Create: Pineapples","Ever wanted pineapples in Minecraft... NOW YOU CAN! This mod adds pinecones, crushed pinecones and even pineapples with its juice!","Introducing the new, fantastic create mod add-on! This mod adds lots of different unique features! E.g:\n-You can make pineapples out of pinecones and apples\n-You can crush pinecones to get experience and spikes\n-A new mysterious liquid (pineapple juice) that gives you a special effect\n\n*Updates that could come:\n-Automated pinecone farming\n-Mugolio (pinecone syrup)\n\nThanks for downloading! :)","2025-11-30T10:31:25.154878Z","2025-11-30T11:00:40.642019Z","2025-12-02T02:17:28.920285Z","2025-11-30T11:02:20.403616Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},614,[93,131,288],[],[354],[31401],"oNRmikua","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T42LHFbj/53d32e0fe61563ede2897fb5107bf1d277771756_96.webp",[],[31405,31411,31417,31423],{"url":31406,"raw_url":31407,"featured":439,"title":31408,"description":31409,"created":31410,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T42LHFbj/images/53d32e0fe61563ede2897fb5107bf1d277771756_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T42LHFbj/images/53d32e0fe61563ede2897fb5107bf1d277771756.png","Mod logo","Nothing special... Do you like it?","2025-11-30T10:40:01.137893Z",{"url":31412,"raw_url":31413,"featured":439,"title":31414,"description":31415,"created":31416,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T42LHFbj/images/75aef175cbb3aba3bf9c8eb487ffa27918e31e14_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T42LHFbj/images/75aef175cbb3aba3bf9c8eb487ffa27918e31e14.png","Items","All the items!\n*Will add more!","2025-11-30T10:42:51.152972Z",{"url":31418,"raw_url":31419,"featured":439,"title":31420,"description":31421,"created":31422,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T42LHFbj/images/83838b8382d00be74e54023ea27a00f432de6dcf_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T42LHFbj/images/83838b8382d00be74e54023ea27a00f432de6dcf.png","Pineapple Juice","Mmm.... Tasty!","2025-11-30T10:50:35.703313Z",{"url":31424,"raw_url":31425,"featured":439,"title":31426,"description":31427,"created":31428,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T42LHFbj/images/efe5092d40f01724577b92713dfefc182c71e406_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T42LHFbj/images/efe5092d40f01724577b92713dfefc182c71e406.png","Glistening Pineapple","What could it do? how do you get it?","2025-11-30T10:51:19.364377Z",5987335,"3AG8RgAq",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31432,"id":31433,"slug":31434,"project_type":31,"team":31435,"organization":3592,"title":31436,"description":31437,"body":31438,"body_url":3592,"published":31439,"updated":31440,"approved":31441,"queued":31442,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31443,"downloads":31444,"followers":29999,"categories":31445,"additional_categories":31446,"loaders":31447,"versions":31448,"icon_url":31488,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":31489,"donation_urls":31490,"gallery":31491,"color":31515,"thread_id":31516,"monetization_status":30002},[1049,1043,847,841,793,790,760,712,670,661,655,610,604,559,505,499,487],"T3n5iJdE","epicka-rpgmounts-for-servers","DvwILQOL","RpgMounts for servers","Utility mod for servers that makes it easy to add a mount system using existing in-game entities.","**Description**\n\nThis utility mod, primarily designed for servers but also compatible with singleplayer and LAN, allows you to turn existing entities into mounts.\n\nEntities will lose their original AI, which is replaced by a simplified one to make them usable as basic mounts.\n\n \n\n📦 **Items**\n\n**Item Namer** – Lets you get an entity’s ID by right-clicking it. Useful for commands.\n\n**Item Mounter** – Ride an entity without controlling it.\n\n**Speed Mount Boost** - A consumable item to boost your mount’s speed.\n\n\n\n📃 **Commands** \n\n```\n/rpgmounts addmount \u003Cplayer_name> \u003Centity_id> \u003CcustomName> \u003CspeedModifier> \u003Ctype>\n```\nUnlocks a mount for a player to use.\n\n```\n/rpgmounts addbyview \u003Cplayer_name> \u003CcustomName> \u003CspeedModifier> \u003Ctype>\n```\nUnlocks a mount by view for a player to use.\n\n```\n/rpgmounts delmount \u003Cplayer_name> \u003Centity_name>\n```\nDelete a previously unlocked mount.\n\n```\n/rpgmounts setenabled \u003Cplayer_name> \u003Centity_name> \u003Ctrue / false>\n```\nDisables a previously unlocked mount.\n\n```\n/rpgmounts menu\n```\nOpens the mount menu without needing the keybind.\n\n```\n/rpgmounts listmounts\n```\nLists all available entities that can be used as mounts.\n\n```\n/rpgmounts credits\n```\nShows simple credits — I made this mod for free, so this is my small way of getting recognition.\n\n```\n/rpgmounts setdesc \u003Cplayer_name> \u003Centity_name> \u003Cdescription>\n```\nAdd description\n\n```\n/rpgmounts cleardesc \u003Cplayer_name> \u003Centity_name>\n```\nClear description\n\n```\n/rpgmounts setcost \u003Cplayer_name> \u003Centity_name> \u003Citem_id> \u003Ccount>\n```\nAdd item cost to spawn the mount\n\n```\n/rpgmounts clearcost \u003Cplayer_name> \u003Centity_name>\n```\nClear the cost\n\n```\n/rpgmounts setspeed \u003Cplayer_name> \u003Centity_name> \u003Cspeed>\n```\nModify mount speed\n\n```\n/rpgmounts giveunlocker \u003Cplayer_name> \u003Centity_id> \u003CcustomName> \u003CspeedModifier> \u003Ctype>\n```\nCreate a mount-unlocking item\n\n```\n/rpgmounts setparticle \u003Cplayer_name> \u003Centity_name> \u003Cparticle_type> \u003Camount>\n```\nCustom particle type when mount spawning\n\nAll commands require operator permissions.\n\nCommand autocompletion has been added to make usage easier.\n\n \n\n🛠 **Keybind**\n\nA keybind called \"Open Menu\" is available under the \"RpgMounts\" category.\nPlayers will mainly need this to access the mount system.\n\nQuick-mount and dismount keybinds are also available.\n\n \n\n⚙️ **Configuration**\n\nA configuration file named epicka-common.toml can be found in the config folder. It allows you to adjust mount behavior and customize parts of the interface.\n\nPlayer data is stored in the epicka subfolder, which tracks unlocked mounts and their activation status.\n\n \n\n📜 **Informations**\n\nThe mod’s optimization and security have been carefully designed to ensure smooth use on large servers. It’s fully functional as it stands, with new content being added over time.\nIf you're interested in using it or feel some features are missing, feel free to contact me, I'm open to feedback and suggestions ! Join my Discord or contact me directely via Modrinth.","2025-10-22T10:59:11.871808Z","2026-04-21T16:29:15.278359Z","2025-10-27T05:10:12.723476Z","2025-10-24T11:40:10.435683Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},739,[134,191,297],[],[354,385],[31449,31450,31451,31452,31453,31454,31455,31456,31457,31458,31459,31460,31461,31462,31463,31464,31465,31466,31467,31468,31469,31470,31471,31472,31473,31474,31475,31476,31477,31478,31479,31480,31481,31482,31483,31484,31485,31486,31487],"mFpRmmJZ","evvU7Ncj","XfSWv5Ld","va1ooGum","npo2Zgmb","5UQFu5zH","UroYKjC6","sLMpLw2e","hgirbDUk","8IjbwKaH","xPbpUalQ","GjoHUE9f","cmu67ANW","R1Hcvkax","HKiPT2Ep","7r1E974U","LHFbHXxO","OLhwJZAR","6Drkwb4D","TIlYnBmd","VuabRs4a","jyXwa5Lk","WFq0vIkx","enNnMlO3","fnHOQPb6","SFWEsDC1","J9BIdavP","Klkv6hnL","ZdtLd7G3","gyxLDKpb","etTNXs78","ZbDVTVWv","brmcapK5","mk3MNGmF","BQgYnpG7","r48d4V88","6DZaGYs9","mQ7pvk45","O0WR55F0","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3n5iJdE/b42c86e163cb4da1fd5d8e471674dff1433d6a55_96.webp","https://discord.gg/XHhacEpJeG",[],[31492,31498,31503,31509],{"url":31493,"raw_url":31494,"featured":439,"title":31495,"description":31496,"created":31497,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3n5iJdE/images/a34e23e3cd4811708a0f4a1a51354920b15a5785_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3n5iJdE/images/a34e23e3cd4811708a0f4a1a51354920b15a5785.png","Default UI","Default UI, fully customizable","2026-02-14T14:11:52.799017Z",{"url":31499,"raw_url":31499,"featured":849,"title":31500,"description":31501,"created":31502,"ordering":29981},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3n5iJdE/images/8921dce0253d76736d0529a34b9c8521b9481197.png","Custom UI","Custom UI made using the configuration options and additional textures (Fantasy Minimal Pixel Art by etahoshi)","2025-11-23T11:18:50.299764Z",{"url":31504,"raw_url":31505,"featured":439,"title":31506,"description":31507,"created":31508,"ordering":29987},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3n5iJdE/images/c2221a91dff4c06a4f96cb23a894b52259842383_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3n5iJdE/images/c2221a91dff4c06a4f96cb23a894b52259842383.png","Modern UI","UI enabled through the enableModernUi option and fully customizable","2026-02-14T14:19:15.882462Z",{"url":31510,"raw_url":31511,"featured":439,"title":31512,"description":31513,"created":31514,"ordering":29993},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3n5iJdE/images/44fdde981dc3f6385ddbac8a2d32c2a463678fe6_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3n5iJdE/images/44fdde981dc3f6385ddbac8a2d32c2a463678fe6.png","Configuration","Mod configuration that you must configure to best meet your needs (Everything didn’t fit in the image, so this is only part of it)","2025-10-22T11:38:09.738539Z",7572608,"CeTSm3QN",{"client_side":29949,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31518,"id":31519,"slug":31520,"project_type":31,"team":31521,"organization":3592,"title":31522,"description":31523,"body":31524,"body_url":3592,"published":31525,"updated":31526,"approved":31527,"queued":31528,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31529,"downloads":31530,"followers":30384,"categories":31531,"additional_categories":31532,"loaders":31533,"versions":31534,"icon_url":31543,"issues_url":31544,"source_url":31545,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":31546,"donation_urls":31547,"gallery":31550,"color":31558,"thread_id":31559,"monetization_status":30002},[712,670,661,655,610,604,559],"T3vt10wr","fantazs-emerald-equipment","UBQMbfju","Emerald Equipment","Adds emerald tools, weapons, and armor to Minecraft","# 💚 Emerald Equipment ⛏️\n\nExpand your Minecraft arsenal with a complete emerald equipment tier! This datapack and resource pack combo adds craftable emerald tools, weapons, and armor that fill the gap between iron and diamond gear.\n![Fantaz and his nautilus wearing emerald gear](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3vt10wr/images/13bd509d5ad2f69254007a5aeb93dd8d165c0d60.png)\n\n---\n\n## ✨ Features\n\n### 🛠️ Complete Equipment Set\nCraft a full set of emerald equipment using emeralds you've gathered from mining or trading:\n\n\u003Cdetails>\n\u003Csummary>\u003Cb>Available Items\u003C/b>\u003C/summary>\n\n- **Tools**: Pickaxe, Axe, Shovel, Hoe\n- **Weapons**: Spear, Sword\n- **Armor**: Helmet, Chestplate, Leggings, Boots\n- **Mounts Armor**: Nautilus Armor, Horse Armor\n\n*All items feature custom textures and full armor trim support!*\n\n\u003C/details>\n\n---\n\n### ⚖️ Balanced Mid-Tier Stats\n\nEmerald equipment sits comfortably between iron and diamond, offering a meaningful upgrade without overshadowing end-game gear:\n\n| Stat | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| **Tools/Weapon Durability** | 960 |\n| **Armor Protection** | 19 Armor, 1 Armor Toughness |\n| **Horse Armor** | 8 Armor, 1 Armor Toughness |\n| **Nautilus Armor** | 7 Armor, 1 Armor Toughness |\n| **Enchantability** | 12 |\n\n---\n\n### ⚔️ Custom Tool Stats\n\nEach tool and weapon has been carefully balanced to feel distinct and useful.\n\n---\n\n### 🎨 Full Armor Trim Support\n\nAll armor pieces support vanilla armor trims!\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 Installation\n\n**For Datapack + Resource Pack:**\n1. Download both the **Datapack** and **Resource Pack** files\n2. Place the datapack ZIP in your world's `datapacks/` folder\n3. Place the resource pack ZIP in your `resourcepacks/` folder and enable it in-game\n4. Reload with `/reload` or restart your world\n\n**For Mod Loaders (Fabric/Forge/NeoForge/Quilt):**\n- Download the `.jar` file and place it in your `mods/` folder\n- *Requires Fabric API for Fabric/Quilt*\n\n---\n\n## 💎 The \"Scrappy Underdog\" Philosophy\n\n> Emerald equipment is designed as the **practical mid-tier choice**: durable enough to be your everyday gear, protective enough to handle most challenges, and enchantable enough to customize to your playstyle. \n> \n> *It's not as flashy as diamond, but it gets the job done and plays nice with your enchanting table.*\n\n---\n\n## 💜 More Equipment Tiers\n\n**Also check out:** \n- **[Amethyst Equipment](https://modrinth.com/datapack/fantazs-amethyst-equipment)** - A companion pack adding amethyst gear to complete your mid-tier options!\n\n---\n\n## 🙏 Credits & Inspiration\n\nThis datapack was inspired by and builds upon:\n- **[Emerald Equipment](https://modrinth.com/mod/emerald-equipment)** © exline – MIT License\n\n*Ported to datapack format with custom balance adjustments and full armor trim support.*\n\n---\n\n## 📝 License & Usage\n\n- *Licensed under MIT.*\n- *Free to use in modpacks and videos with credit.*\n\n---","2025-12-23T01:09:38.054137Z","2026-03-16T17:15:03.495116Z","2025-12-24T10:04:57.819727Z","2025-12-23T02:41:13.492188Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},11595,[115],[],[342,346,354,385,409],[31535,31536,31537,31538,31539,31540,31541,31542],"sU8g8wEw","dTfE27Dz","CcobzKNP","4kuvT12O","eudqM9zx","CLVTWSJC","DkcHRNIx","3rraTtku","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3vt10wr/7a82f98b56f9d9fc6d6e6288245f020cffea594d.png","https://github.com/FaNt4zMa/emerald-equipment/issues","https://github.com/FaNt4zMa/emerald-equipment","https://discord.gg/atukJ6qJaQ",[31548],{"id":3149,"platform":3150,"url":31549},"https://ko-fi.com/fantaz",[31551,31555],{"url":31552,"raw_url":31553,"featured":849,"title":3592,"description":3592,"created":31554,"ordering":29981},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3vt10wr/images/13bd509d5ad2f69254007a5aeb93dd8d165c0d60_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3vt10wr/images/13bd509d5ad2f69254007a5aeb93dd8d165c0d60.png","2025-12-29T08:52:50.410907Z",{"url":31556,"raw_url":31556,"featured":439,"title":3592,"description":3592,"created":31557,"ordering":29987},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3vt10wr/images/f89949743124a6a3e70bdf5397e43b857d929e39.webp","2025-12-29T08:52:36.479880Z",9211020,"OhK9Ig9k",{"client_side":29949,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31561,"id":31562,"slug":31563,"project_type":31,"team":31564,"organization":3592,"title":31565,"description":31566,"body":31567,"body_url":3592,"published":31568,"updated":31569,"approved":31570,"queued":31571,"status":29937,"requested_status":29939,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31572,"downloads":31573,"followers":31574,"categories":31575,"additional_categories":31576,"loaders":31577,"versions":31578,"icon_url":31605,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":31606,"gallery":31607,"color":31608,"thread_id":31562,"monetization_status":30002},[1394,1376,1313,1298,1271,1214,1181,1172,1136,1097,1049,1043,1010,968,962,890,884,847,841,793,790,760,757,754],"T3niFhcB","infinite-totem","3iOZzN1l","Totem of Infinity","God powers","## Currently it does NOT work for 1.21.5 - I might fix it eventually\n\nA datapack and mod where you can have a singular totem be infinite. All you have to do is yeet a totem and an infinity book on the ground and it will merge and then boom, you now have a totem of infinity.\n\n[Curseforge](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/totem-of-infinity)\n\n**Note**\n\nI took down the 1.13-1.16.5 versions because I want to just have the datapack work for later versions.","2023-05-10T20:43:34.633238Z","2025-01-19T04:28:48.153691Z","2023-05-12T00:11:55.348278Z","2023-05-10T20:51:41.334367Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},42985,79,[115,134,303],[171],[342,346,354,385,409],[31579,31580,31581,31582,31583,31584,31585,31586,31587,31588,31589,31590,31591,31592,31593,31594,31595,31596,31597,31598,31599,31600,31601,31602,31603,31604],"8DQWBp0A","7MaaBcho","8RbMZwll","tNeZKrMY","xCgLO8T6","lfjrbVmX","AKeTyyhV","QT3NdQzz","PfiGGgH6","UGSWXNCI","SFEKBiOv","LRRbPcEw","zwkPjeRN","Ov20ZydK","HEnkK56z","ckV946HL","aemHiqCG","rCcdGsL1","TMgJ7nry","QaOe3VnM","Kth6RwY1","WM22QaFB","Nlr30EQ3","dNkFlqiH","3LZligR8","PyEafZr2","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3niFhcB/595c25de5a4f73e42c3eee10ae5f44abe9577670.png",[],[],11696183,{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31610,"id":31611,"slug":31612,"project_type":31,"team":31613,"organization":3592,"title":31614,"description":31615,"body":31616,"body_url":3592,"published":31617,"updated":31618,"approved":31619,"queued":31620,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31621,"downloads":31624,"followers":30075,"categories":31625,"additional_categories":31626,"loaders":31627,"versions":31628,"icon_url":31630,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":31631,"gallery":31632,"color":31246,"thread_id":31639,"monetization_status":30002},[962],"T30ehgkc","noverbs-sword-pack","1oUAGPYZ","Noverb's Sword Pack","Simple Sword Pack Nothing special","### **_Noverb's Sword Pack_**\n\nthis pack is ideal for pvp or fun, there are 16 swords and 1 of them are unobtainable and overpowered with full potencial to one hit every entety!\nSwords can be crafted with gems or vanila elements like:\n\nwither star (smelting) Mining (gems) and so much more!\n\n### **_Swords:_**\n\n- NoTexture (9999 damage and 99 swing speed only creative)\n- Achery Sword (12.8 damage Attack speed 1.6)\n- Devils Blade (9 damage attack speed 2.6)\n- Ruby Knife (9.7 Damage 2.8 attack speed)\n- Zapper Knife (9.5 damage attack speed 2.4)\n- RGB Sword (ANIMATED TEXTURES) (10.5 damage attack speed 3.6)\n- Stovner Sword (8.5 damage attack speed 2.31)\n\nSlowly Begining Overpowered...\n  \n- Stardust Sword (13.5 damage attack speed 1)\n- NoTexture (9999 damage and 99 swing speed only creative)\n- Spyral Sword (21.5 damage attack speed 4.2)\n- Venomshank Sword (27.5 damage attack speed 3.2)\n- Radical Sword (30.2 damage attack speed 3.2)\n- Outer Sword (34.2 attack speed 6.4) (HAS ABILITY ON RIGHT CLICK)\n- Aeron Petastron (27.9 damage attack speed 2.3)\n\nOkay its to far tbh...\n\n- Aero Sword (45.5 damage 3.4 attack speed)\n- Ethernal Sword (56.4 damage attack speed 5.6)\n- Vexoplion Sword (34.9 damage attack speed 7.8)\n\n(that list took to long)\n\n### **_Items:_**\n\n- Acheron Gem (for almost every weapon)\n- Outer Ball (fire ball of outer Sword)\n- Zapper Gem (for venomshanks and the zapper knife)\n- Ruby Gem (for almost every weapon)\n\n","2026-01-31T17:15:20.943428Z","2026-01-31T17:19:38.401020Z","2026-02-03T06:08:00.906393Z","2026-02-01T19:00:43.850931Z",{"id":31622,"name":31623,"url":3592},"BSD-2-Clause","BSD 2-Clause \"Simplified\" License",31,[115],[],[385],[31629],"aCmhHM7V","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T30ehgkc/f3a43e37ab4bbb7cc6e9e2db681709fd3d0cf3cf_96.webp",[],[31633],{"url":31634,"raw_url":31635,"featured":849,"title":31636,"description":31637,"created":31638,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T30ehgkc/images/a5b7419dc25497c5498dbeba146b926e3e909253_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T30ehgkc/images/a5b7419dc25497c5498dbeba146b926e3e909253.png","Preview","Swords & gems","2026-01-31T17:20:34.414679Z","6WKT6033",{"client_side":30037,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31641,"id":31642,"slug":31643,"project_type":31,"team":31644,"organization":3592,"title":31643,"description":31645,"body":31646,"body_url":3592,"published":31647,"updated":31648,"approved":31649,"queued":31650,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31651,"downloads":31652,"followers":30075,"categories":31653,"additional_categories":31654,"loaders":31655,"versions":31656,"icon_url":31658,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":31659,"gallery":31660,"color":31661,"thread_id":31662,"monetization_status":30002},[847,841,793,790,760,712,670,661,655],"T3Fz6zYS","pluginuploader","pRlo1ADo","This is a custome plugin with that you can upload custome plugin with the direct download link. \n\ncommand: /pluginupload \u003Clink>","This is a custom Minecraft plugin designed to make managing your server easier and more flexible. With PluginUploader, you can add new plugins directly to your server without the need to manually download them, move files, or restart your server multiple times. The plugin simplifies the process by allowing you to use a single command to download and store plugins from direct download links.\n\nTo use the plugin, simply type /pluginupload \u003Clink> in the server console or as a player with the appropriate permissions. The link must point to a direct .jar file of the plugin you want to add. PluginUploader supports standard direct download links, Google Drive links, and other hosting services. Google Drive links are automatically converted into direct download links to ensure the plugin is downloaded correctly.\n\nAfter running the command, the plugin file is saved in your server’s plugins folder. The system performs several checks to make sure the downloaded file is a valid JAR, preventing errors from corrupted or invalid downloads. Additionally, it provides a clickable message with the corrected link if any adjustments are needed.\n\nPluginUploader is ideal for server owners who frequently add or update plugins, making plugin management faster, safer, and more convenient. This plugin streamlines your workflow and reduces the risk of errors, giving you more time to focus on running and enjoying your Minecraft plugin.","2025-09-19T13:43:28.740179Z","2025-09-19T13:46:37.217435Z","2025-09-22T05:51:19.080328Z","2025-09-19T13:59:27.588750Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},58,[175],[],[329,401,405,417],[31657],"nVBNZH0b","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3Fz6zYS/2b7a757d4b84419d3afdf8db45086321a73670a2_96.webp",[],[],2955844,"yDLlZgtU",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":30037,"game_versions":31664,"id":31665,"slug":31666,"project_type":34,"team":31667,"organization":3592,"title":31668,"description":31669,"body":31670,"body_url":3592,"published":31671,"updated":31672,"approved":31673,"queued":31674,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31675,"downloads":30095,"followers":29981,"categories":31676,"additional_categories":31677,"loaders":31678,"versions":31679,"icon_url":31681,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":31682,"gallery":31683,"color":31692,"thread_id":31693,"monetization_status":30002},[841],"T43YZaQQ","vildmarken-full","vbpUQMR2","Vildmarken (Full)","For use on our server.\n\nBased on an updated Fabulously Optimized 6.2.3","This modpack is just meant for users of our server, but anyone can use it if they want to.\n\nBased on [Fabulously Optimized](https://modrinth.com/modpack/fabulously-optimized) 6.2.3 with some updated and added QoL mods.\nSpecifically do this modpack enable use of distant horizons with shaders.\n\nMods updated:\n* Iris (1.8.1)\n* MoreCulling (1.0.1)\n* Sodium (0.6.2)\n* Sodium Extra (0.6.0)\n\nMods added:\n* Antique Atlas\n* Appleskin\n* ArmorStatues\n* BadhorseFix\n* BetterPingDisplay\n* Bobby\n* Distant Horizons (2.2.1-a)\n* Gravelminer\n* InventoryTweaks\n* Jade\n* JadeAddons\n* Jade: Your Reputation\n* JEI\n* Name Visibility\n* No Telemetry\n* PhysicsMod\n* WaveyCapes\n* (and dependencies of above)\n\n\nReese's Sodium Options have been removed, as it is not ready for the newer versions of the other updated mods.","2024-12-07T07:03:12.133299Z","2024-12-07T07:18:20.350843Z","2024-12-09T08:52:45.048521Z","2024-12-07T07:38:32.946796Z",{"id":30698,"name":30699,"url":3592},[153],[],[346],[31680],"PlYIU6CV","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T43YZaQQ/b24e87839c4cd8debea83720d9b4a618b64bb3d0.png",[],[31684,31688],{"url":31685,"raw_url":31686,"featured":849,"title":3592,"description":3592,"created":31687,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T43YZaQQ/images/8444174b87ea60710326784f16bbef487c875e33_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T43YZaQQ/images/8444174b87ea60710326784f16bbef487c875e33.png","2024-12-07T07:22:40.289018Z",{"url":31689,"raw_url":31690,"featured":439,"title":3592,"description":3592,"created":31691,"ordering":29981},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T43YZaQQ/images/0bdf39b6c98ec03ac239a8a010dba9e681ed8542_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T43YZaQQ/images/0bdf39b6c98ec03ac239a8a010dba9e681ed8542.png","2024-12-07T07:22:50.751267Z",1324164,"H4b3Ifkr",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":30037,"game_versions":31695,"id":31696,"slug":31697,"project_type":34,"team":31698,"organization":3592,"title":31699,"description":31700,"body":31701,"body_url":3592,"published":31702,"updated":31703,"approved":31704,"queued":31705,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31706,"downloads":31707,"followers":30075,"categories":31708,"additional_categories":31709,"loaders":31710,"versions":31711,"icon_url":31713,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":31714,"donation_urls":31715,"gallery":31718,"color":31719,"thread_id":31720,"monetization_status":30002},[841],"T4DHnQjl","project-snowcraft-1.21.1","XxhLeMmg","Project Snowcraft 1.21.1","Lightweight, optimization & QoL focused modpack","NOW UPDATED TO 1.21.1! This modpack DOES NOT have the exact same mods as 1.20.1 and has had most of the quirky mods removed.\n\nThis Modpack is *INTENDED* to be **USED WITH OPTIFINE** :)\n\nA lightweight, optimization focused modpack, with QoL & fun mods. This is targeted for both client & server usage.\n\nThis pack is currently developed by myself, with the interaction & feedback of my friends, on a private SMP server.\n\n---\n\nAbout this pack:\n\nThis pack contains our ideas of 'essential' mods, the main focus is QoL & high framerates, and attempting to be as lightweight as possible, for an average server, which was later upgraded to a slightly better server.\n\nThis SMP pack is still in early development and is currently stable.\nThis pack is developed in Singleplayer, but played and experienced entirely on a Multiplayer (SMP) server.\n\nIf anyone would like to give feedback please feel free to reach out to me on discord. Balancing is hard :p\n\n---\n\nRequirements:\n- Minimum: Alright CPU & 4GB+ RAM (As much as can be allocated in Modrinth Settings)\n- Recommended: Decent CPU & 8GB+ RAM (Max allocatable is optimal)\n\nWe always recommend you to use the latest version.\n\n---\n\nFor Server Creators: (these are found in the server.properties file)\n\n- The spawn protection range of the server, that prevents players from digging or opening doors, is set in the server.properties file and has been set to: (spawn protection: 1).\n- I have also turned watchdog off (max-tick-time: -1) to prevent idle server crashes/the sever becoming unresponsive.","2024-09-22T21:34:50.910418Z","2024-09-22T21:35:32.352161Z","2024-09-24T19:03:08.730866Z","2024-09-22T21:45:35.271052Z",{"id":30732,"name":30733,"url":3592},394,[162,200,211],[30],[346],[31712],"yuysMTti","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4DHnQjl/6c1ac4a23a7b4eb963baa2b5256c2304341fc44d.png","https://discord.gg/HcKG6XKwQT",[31716],{"id":3143,"platform":30113,"url":31717},"https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted_button_id=DTCLLZW8M83DW",[],13077803,"epyYdH0L",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31722,"id":31723,"slug":31724,"project_type":31,"team":31725,"organization":3592,"title":31726,"description":31727,"body":31728,"body_url":3592,"published":31729,"updated":31730,"approved":31731,"queued":3592,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31732,"downloads":31733,"followers":30366,"categories":31734,"additional_categories":31735,"loaders":31736,"versions":31737,"icon_url":31759,"issues_url":31760,"source_url":31761,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":31762,"gallery":31763,"color":31764,"thread_id":31723,"monetization_status":30002},[1136,1103,1097,1049,1043,847],"T4Cf7c9y","quilt-tag-plus","jJfxbpMC","Quilt Tag Plus","This mod adds several tags to improve the control of some basic Minecraft features.","# Quilt Tag Plus\n\n\n\nThis mod adds several tags to improve the control of some basic Minecraft features.\n\nThis can be usefull for compatibility (this avoids possible conflicts with Mixin).\n\n## Content\n\n### Block Tags\n\n**Block Tags are located in `data/quilt_tag_plus/tags/block` folder**\n\n- `azalea_plantable_on` which controls which blocks azalea's can be placed on\n- `chorus_plantable_on` which controls which blocks a chorus plant can be placed on\n- `end_crystal_use_on` which controls which blocks an End Crystal can be used\n- `nether_wart_plantable_on` which controls which blocks a nether wart can be placed on\n- `not_pushable_by_piston` which controls which blocks cannot be pushed by a piston\n- `sugar_cane_plantable_on` which controls which blocks a sugar cane can be placed on\n- `seagrass_cant_plant_on` which controls which blocks a seagrass can't be placed on\n- `wither_rose_plantable_on` which controls which blocks a wither rose can be placed on\n\n### Item Tags\n\n**Item Tags are located in `data/quilt_tag_plus/tags/item` folder**\n\n- `elytra_repair_ingredients` which controls which items can be used to repair elytra\n- `iron_golem_healing` which controls which items can be used to heal Iron Golem\n- `minecart_furnace_fuel` which controls which items can be used for Minecart with Furnace\n- `respawn_anchor_charges` which controls which items can be used to fill respawn anchor\n- `tnt_igniters` which controls which items can be used to ignite Tnt Block\n\n## Credits\n\n- Logo by [QuiltMC](https://quiltmc.org) : https://github.com/QuiltMC/art\n","2023-02-05T18:09:55.084668Z","2024-07-21T20:18:48.306511Z","2023-02-18T01:18:28.403800Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},4727,[157],[],[409],[31738,31739,31740,31741,31742,31743,31744,31745,31746,31747,31748,31749,31750,31751,31752,31753,31754,31755,31756,31757,31758],"D5bOyGRR","agal9708","Idt7AoQe","mmJc6WmM","Bcs3sX1x","Zh86eqwC","xgAMzQz2","jp4vBJs7","a3kzLjhp","Yll4UnFo","97UgGQJC","ognVbW9E","d9cyFn5N","dH6qvpor","hARqOvdt","yFkoWDx0","HAyD71uj","Jtjv5TrS","GqA8O5lE","JJJcsMW9","SSId0tmm","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4Cf7c9y/2f14bc27d1a22fe229de7385671e7f42b0a76c19_96.webp","https://github.com/Arthur-GYT/Quilt-Tag-Plus/issues","https://github.com/Arthur-GYT/Quilt-Tag-Plus",[],[],3556348,{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31766,"id":31767,"slug":31768,"project_type":31,"team":31769,"organization":3592,"title":31770,"description":31771,"body":31772,"body_url":3592,"published":31773,"updated":31774,"approved":31775,"queued":31776,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31777,"downloads":31779,"followers":29987,"categories":31780,"additional_categories":31781,"loaders":31782,"versions":31783,"icon_url":31786,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":31787,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":31788,"donation_urls":31789,"gallery":31792,"color":31799,"thread_id":31800,"monetization_status":30002},[847,841,793,790,760,712,670,661,655],"T31dVExP","pre-placement-block-rotation","ocwW22MZ","Pre-Placement Block Rotation","A client-side mod that lets you manually rotate and flip blocks before placing them, bypassing Minecraft's strict placement rules.","![Pre-Placement-Block-Rotation](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dev-jcwd/Pre-Placement-Block-Rotation/main/BANNER.gif)  \n\n![Fabric Only](https://img.shields.io/badge/Loader-Fabric-blue?logo=fabricmc&logoColor=white)\n![Client Side](https://img.shields.io/badge/Environment-Client--Side-green)\n![MC Versions](https://img.shields.io/badge/Minecraft-1.21%20→%201.21.9-yellow)\n\n[![Join Discord](https://img.shields.io/badge/Discord-Join%20Community-5865F2?logo=discord&logoColor=white)](https://discord.gg/TubuNkwPam)\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ BETA NOTICE\n\nThis mod is currently in **Beta**.\n\nThe current release is **Singleplayer Only**.\n\nWe are actively working on making the system compatible with **Multiplayer servers**, but due to how Minecraft handles block placement and synchronization, additional work is required.\n\nUntil then, please treat this version as **experimental**.\n\nExpect:\n• Possible bugs  \n• Incomplete block compatibility  \n• Future improvements  \n\nYour feedback helps a lot!\n\n---\n\n# 🧱 What This Mod Does\n\nEver struggled to place an **Observer**, **Piston**, or **Stair** facing the exact direction you want?\n\nVanilla Minecraft often forces you to:\n\n• Look in specific directions  \n• Build temporary scaffolding  \n• Place blocks multiple times just to get the correct orientation  \n\n**Pre-Placement Block Rotation** removes those restrictions.\n\nRotate and flip blocks **before placing them**, giving you full control over orientation — even when looking straight up, straight down, or from awkward angles.\n\nNo more dirt towers.  \nNo more breaking and replacing blocks.  \n\nJust **place it correctly the first time.**\n\n---\n\n# ✨ Features\n\n## 👻 Perfect Sync Ghost Preview\nSee exactly how the block will be placed **before clicking**.\n\nA translucent preview shows the **final rotation and orientation** in real time so you know exactly what you're placing.\n\n---\n\n## 🔓 Breaks Vanilla Direction Locks\n\nMinecraft normally locks certain blocks depending on where you're looking.\n\nThis mod bypasses those restrictions.\n\nExample:\n\nLook straight down → place an **Observer facing North**.\n\nNo scaffolding required.\n\n---\n\n## 🧱 Universal Block Support\n\nWorks with most directional blocks including:\n\n• Observers  \n• Pistons  \n• Dispensers  \n• Logs & Pillars  \n• Stairs  \n• Slabs  \n• Chests  \n• Furnaces  \n• Many more vanilla blocks\n\n---\n\n## ⚡ Quick Toggle\n\nEnable or disable the mod instantly whenever you need it.\n\nNo menus required.\n\n---\n\n# 🎮 Default Controls\n\nAll controls can be changed in:\n\n**Minecraft → Options → Controls → Rotation Placement**\n\n| Key | Action |\n|----|------|\n| **R** | Toggle Mod ON / OFF |\n| **Right Arrow** | Rotate Block Horizontally |\n| **Up Arrow** | Flip Block Vertically |\n\n---\n\n# ⚙️ Compatibility\n\n✔ Fabric Loader required  \n✔ Client-side mod  \n✔ Safe to install on servers (but functionality is **singleplayer only for now**)  \n\nSupported Minecraft versions:\n\n**1.21 → 1.21.9**\n\n---\n\n# 💡 Perfect For\n\n• Redstone engineers  \n• Technical builders  \n• Creative builders  \n• Anyone tired of Minecraft's placement restrictions  \n\nBuild faster and place blocks **exactly how you want**.\n\nWant to request a mod for free? Join the [Discord Server](https://discord.gg/TubuNkwPam)  \n","2026-03-15T20:42:56.992912Z","2026-03-16T10:03:47.289110Z","2026-03-25T02:26:29.949932Z","2026-03-16T10:42:47.990809Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":31778},"https://github.com/dev-jcwd/Pre-Placement-Block-Rotation/blob/main/LICENSE",118,[134,303],[],[346],[31784,31785],"cD1BHTPK","S2EkabFz","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T31dVExP/68811da50c97f9bf0a9fbd94c503406bb1ab5aa7_96.webp","https://github.com/dev-jcwd/Pre-Placement-Block-Rotation/tree/main","https://discord.gg/TubuNkwPam",[31790],{"id":3149,"platform":3150,"url":31791},"https://ko-fi.com/qof_jcwd",[31793],{"url":31794,"raw_url":31795,"featured":849,"title":31796,"description":31797,"created":31798,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T31dVExP/images/a7261385c614d3215179f9ca37f0cce2bdb9c5c0_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T31dVExP/images/a7261385c614d3215179f9ca37f0cce2bdb9c5c0.jpeg","Block Rotation Preview","Allows you to see where your block is facing before placing!","2026-03-16T10:19:18.684714Z",9533257,"g3M1ZPMX",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31802,"id":31803,"slug":31804,"project_type":34,"team":31805,"organization":3592,"title":31806,"description":31807,"body":31808,"body_url":3592,"published":31809,"updated":31810,"approved":31811,"queued":31812,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31813,"downloads":31814,"followers":30075,"categories":31815,"additional_categories":31816,"loaders":31817,"versions":31818,"icon_url":31820,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":31821,"gallery":31822,"color":31848,"thread_id":31849,"monetization_status":30002},[1043],"T4RV6kuN","pyschologicalmess","ZGug0CNX","Pyschological Mess [Horror]","“Sanity is just the beginning.”","  # PHYSCOLOGICAL MESS👁‍\n\"Sanity is just the beginning\"\n\n\u003Cdetails>\n## \u003Csummary>🛑MANUAL INSTALLS RECOMMENDED🛑(for the best experience)\u003C/summary>\n\n**- Excalibur|Corpse** [(Resource Pack)](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/excalibur-corpse-support)\n\n**- Horor Ambience Music** [(Resource Pack)](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/horror-ambience-music)\n\n**- The Masked** [(Mod)](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/disturbed)\n\n\u003C/details>\n\n\n\nMinimum Ram Allocation💾: 4GB\n\nI can assure you that the shaders look a lot better in game!\n- ## Introduction\nMade with the intention of adressing the issue of \"annoying ≠ scary\". I am highly confident in this modpack's horror factor, try it out.\n\n- ## ‼️Features\n  - Customized Spawn Rates\n  - Optimized Experience\n  - Custom Terrain Generation\n  - Lore. (Structural)\n  - Progressive Agressiveness\n  - Custom Tools, Weapons, and Backpacks\n  - Total Immersion & Enhanced Visuals\n  - Added Ambience\n  - Extra QOL features\n  - Custom Shaderpack\n  - Simple Voice Chat\n \n\u003Cdetails>\n\u003Csummary>⛰️Mods Used\u003C/summary>\n\n**- Backpacks** - [Sophisticated Backpacks ](https://modrinth.com/mod/sophisticated-backpacks/versions)\n\n**- Tools** - [Spartan's Weaponry](https://modrinth.com/mod/spartan-weaponry/versions) | [Spartan's Shields](https://modrinth.com/mod/spartan-shields/versions) | [Azure Paxels](https://modrinth.com/mod/azure-paxels)\n\n**- Terrain** - [WWOO](https://modrinth.com/mod/wwoo)\n\u003C/details>\n\n\n\n##  IMPORTANT\n1. This modpack is still in early development and may be buggy. But I'm still working on a way for you guys to report bugs to me, sorry :(\n3. I highly recommend installing the required resource packs and mod, **simple download and drag into either your resources or mod folders.** Thank you\n4. You can also play this pack in multiplayer using Essentials server hosting **(Please make sure you and the person you're playing with has the EXACT same mods or else it will not work)**\n5. I also highly recommend playing this with **all sound on and using the built in shaderpack. (For the full experience and immersion)**\n6. Also it's worth mentioning that this modpack is slow paced and requires patience. Like I said it'll get progressively more agressive\n7. For those who are confused about recipes I have JEI built in.\n8. Play with Voice Chat.. (Keybind configuration is up to you, so I highly recommend checking it)\n\n\nOther than that. Enjoy :)\n\nPlease contact me on @duki.doo on discord to report anything wrong, I'll try my best to help\n\n\n\u003Cdetails>\n\u003Csummary>🛑Spoiler🛑\u003C/summary>\n\n- > [Boy and The Bath](https://modrinth.com/mod/the-bath)\n- > [From The Caves](https://modrinth.com/mod/from-the-cave/versions)\n- > [The Anomally](https://modrinth.com/mod/the-anomaly-rephased)\n- > [The Boiled One](https://modrinth.com/mod/the-boiled-one-reimagined)\n- > [Who's There?[Ghost Players]](https://modrinth.com/mod/whos-there-ghost-players/version/rf6TqFVl)\n- > [The Masked](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/disturbed)\n\n\u003C/details>\n","2025-10-21T01:11:51.416323Z","2025-10-21T06:10:30.289734Z","2025-10-21T14:38:22.358503Z","2025-10-21T04:13:27.444270Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},293,[30,69,162],[200,211],[354],[31819],"NgLtIpKF","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4RV6kuN/4a1f40afacd591902e572b30cda85fd70f48106c_96.webp",[],[31823,31828,31833,31838,31843],{"url":31824,"raw_url":31825,"featured":439,"title":31826,"description":3592,"created":31827,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4RV6kuN/images/13346bbd1aadfed19a3ef4dc195be90368280a68_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4RV6kuN/images/13346bbd1aadfed19a3ef4dc195be90368280a68.png","Forest","2025-10-21T06:38:06.253219Z",{"url":31829,"raw_url":31830,"featured":439,"title":31831,"description":3592,"created":31832,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4RV6kuN/images/49ba71bebcaf385141f46d0e6dfbd63e36645d58_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4RV6kuN/images/49ba71bebcaf385141f46d0e6dfbd63e36645d58.png","Hanging Lanterns","2025-10-21T06:37:40.157402Z",{"url":31834,"raw_url":31835,"featured":439,"title":31836,"description":3592,"created":31837,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4RV6kuN/images/5d09baa22c77cd5e6c398c0408afc2a34e654a60_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4RV6kuN/images/5d09baa22c77cd5e6c398c0408afc2a34e654a60.png","House.?","2025-10-21T06:32:57.004657Z",{"url":31839,"raw_url":31840,"featured":439,"title":31841,"description":3592,"created":31842,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4RV6kuN/images/76ef49bab3a4914d12fdff6226b6473b8413cd9f_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4RV6kuN/images/76ef49bab3a4914d12fdff6226b6473b8413cd9f.png","Watchtower","2025-10-21T06:35:25.015839Z",{"url":31844,"raw_url":31845,"featured":439,"title":31846,"description":3592,"created":31847,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4RV6kuN/images/f03a1302fd3e634215dddee1ae2cf0387d5861a3_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4RV6kuN/images/f03a1302fd3e634215dddee1ae2cf0387d5861a3.png","Subtle Effects","2025-10-21T06:38:37.518979Z",7761004,"huVoxlgH",{"client_side":30037,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31851,"id":31852,"slug":31853,"project_type":31,"team":31854,"organization":3592,"title":31855,"description":31856,"body":31857,"body_url":3592,"published":31858,"updated":31859,"approved":31860,"queued":31861,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31862,"downloads":31863,"followers":29987,"categories":31864,"additional_categories":31865,"loaders":31866,"versions":31867,"icon_url":31870,"issues_url":31871,"source_url":31872,"wiki_url":31873,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":31874,"gallery":31875,"color":31876,"thread_id":31877,"monetization_status":30002},[847,841,793,790,760,712,670,661,655,610,604],"T3GA2RoA","keep_ghastling","bJHBiGn9","Keep_Ghastling","Help ghastling to maintain its juvenile state","\u003Ca herf=\"https://github.com/Data708983/Keep_Ghastling\">\n\u003Cp align=\"center\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/229648d1846314e9dba94887ab3b44943ef9ccdc.gif\" alt=\"Ghastling\">\u003C/p>\n\u003C/a>\n\u003Cp align=\"center\">Help ghastling maintaining its juvenile state\u003C/p>\n\n# \u003Ccenter> Keep_Ghastling\n\n\u003Cp align=\"center\">\n    Give us a star if you like this!\n\u003C/p>\n\n\u003Cp align=\"center\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://github.com/Data708983/Keep_Ghastling/releases\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/downloads/Data708983/Keep_Ghastling/total?color=%239F7AEA\" alt=\"Release Downloads\">\u003C/a>\n  \u003Ca href=\"#\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/repo-size/Data708983/Keep_Ghastling?color=6882C4\" alt=\"GitHub Repo Size\">\u003C/a>\n  \u003Ca href=\"#\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/last-commit/Data708983/Keep_Ghastling?color=%23638e66\" alt=\"Last Commit\">\u003C/a>\n  \u003Ca href=\"#\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/release-date/Data708983/Keep_Ghastling?color=%15\" alt=\"Release Date\">\u003C/a>\n\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp align=\"center\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"#\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/MC_version-1.21.x-blue\" alt=\"MC Version\">\u003C/a>\n\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n## Introduction\n**Keep_Ghastling** is a paper plugin helping ghastling to maintain its juvenile state.\n\n## Features\n- Use **ice blocks** on the Happy Ghastling to fix its juvenile state\n- Use **Magma Cream** on a Happy Ghastling to release it from being fixed\n\n## Building\n\nFeel free to build it yourself when you'd like to try the latest version.\n\nGradle is required to build the project.\n\n\n```sh\ngradle build\n```\n\n---\n- I have to apologize that the 1.0 ver. plugin did't work as expectation due to the misunderstand of the Document. But 2.0 ver. must work well! ❤️\n- Please report bugs and feature requests. PRs are welcome! 🙏🏻","2025-10-31T13:25:54.943081Z","2025-11-05T05:16:16.753882Z","2025-11-02T06:17:23.244323Z","2025-10-31T13:51:39.180452Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},55,[30,191],[100],[401],[31868,31869],"y9FDTiJc","uyiH8Mdo","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3GA2RoA/43ad681a2ea5756bada5116451002faf8ce37f87.png","https://github.com/Data708983/Keep_Ghastling/issues","https://github.com/Data708983/Keep_Ghastling","https://github.com/Data708983/Keep_Ghastling/blob/master/README.md",[],[],9474192,"qOoLWfuX",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":30037,"game_versions":31879,"id":31880,"slug":31881,"project_type":31,"team":31882,"organization":3592,"title":31883,"description":31884,"body":31885,"body_url":3592,"published":31886,"updated":31887,"approved":31888,"queued":31889,"status":29938,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31890,"downloads":31893,"followers":29999,"categories":31894,"additional_categories":31895,"loaders":31896,"versions":31897,"icon_url":31899,"issues_url":31900,"source_url":31901,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":31902,"donation_urls":31903,"gallery":31906,"color":31246,"thread_id":31907,"monetization_status":30002},[2336],"T2u4f9jf","microoptimizations","HPLSr9NF","MicroOptimizations","(Broken) Optimizations for Forge 1.8.9","# This mod currently causes issues!! Since 1.8 is dead these will not be fixed!\n\n\u003Ca href=\"https://ko-fi.com/microcontrollers\" target=\"_blank\">\n  \u003Cimg alt=\"kofi-singular-alt\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/donate/kofi-singular-alt_vector.svg\">\n\u003C/a>\n\n\u003Ca href=\"https://codeberg.org/MicrocontrollersDev/MicroOptimizations\" target=\"_blank\">\n  \u003Cimg alt=\"codeberg\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/codeberg_vector.svg\">\n\u003C/a>\n\n\u003Ca href=\"=https://modrinth.com/mod/oneconfig\" target=\"_blank\">\n  \u003Cimg alt=\"oneconfig\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://polyfrost.org/media/branding/badges/badge_1.svg\">\n\u003C/a>\n\n# MicroOptimizations\n\nFeatherClient has made some of their optimizations public at [FeatherOpt](https://github.com/FeatherMC/FeatherOpt). I ported the optimizations that do not already exist in other Forge 1.8.9 optimization mods here to work on regular Forge. These optimizations are mostly cache and block pos pooling improvements.\n\nFor further optimizations, I recommend using [OptiFine](https://optifine.net/download?f=preview_OptiFine_1.8.9_HD_U_M6_pre2.jar), [PolyPatcher](https://modrinth.com/mod/patcher), [Redirector](https://github.com/MCTeamPotato/Redirector/releases/download/1.4-1.12.2-1.8.8/redirectionor-1.4.for.1.12.2-1.8.8.jar), and [Velox Caelo](https://modrinth.com/mod/veloxcaelo).\n\n## Modpack?\n\nYou may use this mod as the license permits.","2024-08-08T20:11:25.521420Z","2024-08-08T20:12:00.624416Z","2024-08-09T05:17:25.996548Z","2024-08-08T20:18:17.961629Z",{"id":31891,"name":31892,"url":3592},"LGPL-2.1-only","GNU Lesser General Public License v2.1 only",81270,[211],[],[354],[31898],"qH78ug2m","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2u4f9jf/00c9230e9abb9b2d4412ec0420713e574126af78_96.webp","https://codeberg.org/MicrocontrollersDev/MicroOptimizations/issues","https://codeberg.org/MicrocontrollersDev/MicroOptimizations","https://discord.gg/rejfv9kFJj",[31904],{"id":3149,"platform":3150,"url":31905},"https://ko-fi.com/microcontrollers",[],"WCRYZ03j",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":31909,"id":31910,"slug":31911,"project_type":31,"team":31912,"organization":3592,"title":31913,"description":31914,"body":31915,"body_url":3592,"published":31916,"updated":31917,"approved":31918,"queued":31919,"status":29937,"requested_status":29939,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31920,"downloads":31921,"followers":29981,"categories":31922,"additional_categories":31923,"loaders":31924,"versions":31925,"icon_url":31931,"issues_url":31932,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":31933,"gallery":31934,"color":31960,"thread_id":31961,"monetization_status":30002},[1043],"T47AHRs9","tusk-act-4-(jcraft-addon)","CHJcRHrN","Tusk Act 4 (JCraft Addon)","Adds Tusk Act 4 as a stand to JCraft: EOE 0.18.0+ (JOJO, JJBA)","**Adds Tusk Act 4 as a new stand to JCraft 0.18.0+**\n\n**USE \"/stand about\"!**\n\nThis adds an entire new stand to JCraft with custom abilities! He doesn't replace ANY stands and he is an addition to your JCraft!\n\n**This REQUIRES JCraft Additions 1.0.0 or above!**\n\nThis Stand does not have a lore accurate obtaining or evolution; Tusk Act 4 is just drawn at random on use of a stand arrow. \n\nTusk Act 4 was built as a slow, but powerful stand. Though being a short-range stand, he does however feature 2 ranged attacks. The player is able to shoot their nails at the enemy during any attack, locking onto the nearest mob to it. Tusk Act 4 itself also has a charge attack that travels several blocks.\n\nI know people have been begging for Tusk Act 4 in JCraft for a long time so I figured this addon would be nice shared for everybody who wants it. \n\n**I DID NOT MAKE THIS MODEL!** Mr. Garlic, the official model maker for JCraft, gave me this model since they are working on a new Tusk Act 4 model that will eventually be added to JCraft. This addon is more to just have something FOR NOW....\n\nIf you have questions about this mod, MESSAGE ME! The JCraft Devs did not make this mod so they will not be able to help you.\n\nand hopefully for the Steel Block Run server ;)","2026-06-05T18:59:45.215871Z","2026-06-12T22:12:23.787237Z","2026-06-08T01:27:39.100653Z","2026-06-06T01:54:37.341627Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},800,[30,134,303],[100,115],[346,354],[31926,31927,31928,31929,31930],"mr4xgrfl","VGUWUEzm","BjHMzRGw","OjN3xfsf","jeQfnPGH","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T47AHRs9/24a13a9fe16ee0bbdec2347465527d8ac1797545_96.webp","https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc3UxkiRhf5lYdikbi3jNae0msFHBfEO8QeTDlZUFpD0qtsyg/viewform?usp=header",[],[31935,31940,31945,31949,31954],{"url":31936,"raw_url":31937,"featured":439,"title":31938,"description":3592,"created":31939,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T47AHRs9/images/0809abd13c3096e9bb58d8b9ffe251371c6bec30_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T47AHRs9/images/0809abd13c3096e9bb58d8b9ffe251371c6bec30.png","Icon Image","2026-06-06T08:08:15.781080Z",{"url":31941,"raw_url":31942,"featured":849,"title":31943,"description":3592,"created":31944,"ordering":29981},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T47AHRs9/images/2142eda0d3add04ed37c49fad7b94475c17ea2d8_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T47AHRs9/images/2142eda0d3add04ed37c49fad7b94475c17ea2d8.png","Tusk Act 4 Ingame","2026-06-05T19:43:19.583945Z",{"url":31946,"raw_url":31946,"featured":439,"title":31947,"description":3592,"created":31948,"ordering":29987},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T47AHRs9/images/93ecf2466badde40a489f8829752f2efaae7b858.gif","Summon Animation","2026-06-05T19:50:13.520814Z",{"url":31950,"raw_url":31951,"featured":439,"title":31952,"description":3592,"created":31953,"ordering":29993},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T47AHRs9/images/c0ed61fe68b8c63e9bee52e0f65370ca106792e5_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T47AHRs9/images/c0ed61fe68b8c63e9bee52e0f65370ca106792e5.png","Discord 1","2026-06-05T19:48:51.525381Z",{"url":31955,"raw_url":31956,"featured":439,"title":31957,"description":31958,"created":31959,"ordering":29999},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T47AHRs9/images/77bc85637596bd6e76362789140704e38added27_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T47AHRs9/images/77bc85637596bd6e76362789140704e38added27.png","Discord 2","the STRONGEST modeler is Mr. Garlic... a fitting title.","2026-06-05T19:49:32.948837Z",12155573,"Pz7bDYL3",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":30037,"game_versions":31963,"id":31964,"slug":31965,"project_type":12,"team":31966,"organization":3592,"title":31967,"description":31968,"body":31969,"body_url":3592,"published":31970,"updated":31971,"approved":31972,"queued":31973,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":31974,"downloads":31975,"followers":30505,"categories":31976,"additional_categories":31977,"loaders":31978,"versions":31979,"icon_url":31989,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":31990,"donation_urls":31991,"gallery":31992,"color":32061,"thread_id":32062,"monetization_status":30002},[847,841,793,790,760,712,670,661,655,610,604,559,505,499],"T3KUxXJT","leafy-creepers","nRSOvKjE","Leafy Creepers","A Fresh Look at Creepers with Depth and Leaves!","# ![Leafy Creepers](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/a34d8696f9e753e81dccb3b8117484a5b079506f.png)\nThis Resource Pack aims to modernize the Creeper in a way that hasn't yet been thouroughly explored, by updating its' textures to match modern leaf textures, and reinforcing their fantasy.\n\nCreepers will now have two layers, a Leaf layer and a Trunk layer, giving the Creeper more depth and interest. This pack also adds many texture variations of the Creeper for different biomes and environments\n\n![Some Creeper Variants](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/f2186196f23e4d8fe0bc8d3601e3399831773761.png)\n\nThe adjusted creeper design also takes advantage of it's new depth by placing the \"Charged\" aura underneath the Leaf layer\n![Charged Cherry Creeper](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/6222fe47a53bb631e39775fbea376d657bbc6702.png)\n\nTo make the most of this pack, also add the pack to your world's Datapack folder, this will prevent texture variations from changing, perfect for if you want to collect every variant!\n\u003Cbr/>(Requires ETF, Optifine not compatible)\n\n## Compatibility\nVersion 1.1.0 adds support for Modded Biomes, adding 59 new variants, for a total of 85!\n![Terralith Ashen Savanna Creeper](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/0eb3b34d10652071332f39c12b87046d89d34fec.png)\n\u003Cdetails>\n\u003Csummary>All Compatible Biome Mods\u003C/summary>\nTerralith\u003C/br>\nBiomes O' Plenty\u003C/br>\nRegions Unexplored\u003C/br>\nTerrestria\u003C/br>\nNature's Spirit\u003C/br>\nOh The Biomes We've Gone\u003C/br>\nCliff Under A tree\u003C/br>\nBlooming Biosphere\n\u003C/details>\n\nThe FA version of this pack is fully compatible with FreshLX's [Fresh Animations](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/fresh-animations)\n\nIf using shaders it is recommended that labPBR emissives are enabled as some effects may not function correctly otherwise\n\n## Dependencies\nThis Pack requires Entity Texture Features and Entity Model Features\n\n[![Entity Texture Features](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Traben-0/Entity_Texture_Features/master/.github/README-assets/icon.png)](https://modrinth.com/mod/entitytexturefeatures)\n[![Entity Model Features](https://github.com/Traben-0/Entity_Model_Features/blob/master/src/main/resources/icon.png?raw=true)](https://modrinth.com/mod/entity-model-features)\n\nOptifine can be used as an alternative\n\n(All Images Taken while using [Fresh Animations](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/fresh-animations) and [Rethinking Voxels](https://modrinth.com/shader/rethinking-voxels))\n\n\u003Cdetails>\n\u003Csummary>Easter Egg\u003C/summary>\nPale Garden Creepers glow orange when charged\n\n![Charged Pale Garden Creeper](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/341b21672b47244ac27d38c7fbcb71c9d6186d20_0.webp)\n\u003C/details>\n\n","2025-01-24T19:41:40.625650Z","2025-03-26T02:27:19.125144Z","2025-01-25T08:34:24.787940Z","2025-01-25T05:43:06.488507Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},7188,[110,300,307],[15,100,197],[377],[31980,31981,31982,31983,31984,31985,31986,31987,31988],"wAEj4uYb","BnnOVLSn","HJEGinrs","xQpLPtCO","odsVDaqe","cxF44J1O","bvIz1hcp","4Ha178o4","XjbZscqk","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/3e2c2775aa901d54e0e7a271beffd42138fc0058_96.webp","https://discord.gg/T5MGNBB",[],[31993,31999,32004,32009,32014,32019,32024,32029,32034,32040,32045,32050,32055],{"url":31994,"raw_url":31995,"featured":439,"title":31996,"description":31997,"created":31998,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/0eb3b34d10652071332f39c12b87046d89d34fec_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/0eb3b34d10652071332f39c12b87046d89d34fec.png","Ashen Savanna Creeper","For Terralith","2025-02-15T19:08:33.217335Z",{"url":32000,"raw_url":32001,"featured":439,"title":32002,"description":3592,"created":32003,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/0f66bc17f3d9cfbee45743c4a2253c60f0f5e6e0_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/0f66bc17f3d9cfbee45743c4a2253c60f0f5e6e0.png","Jungle Creeper","2025-02-15T19:08:52.795775Z",{"url":32005,"raw_url":32006,"featured":439,"title":32007,"description":3592,"created":32008,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/21f3abba5327211f99a3bec473a9fc18c14a2a06_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/21f3abba5327211f99a3bec473a9fc18c14a2a06.png","Cherry & Oak Creepers","2025-01-25T19:28:22.397233Z",{"url":32010,"raw_url":32011,"featured":439,"title":32012,"description":3592,"created":32013,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/2f3b5239fb6278572c9f91153795553dd60e187c_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/2f3b5239fb6278572c9f91153795553dd60e187c.png","Beach Creeper","2025-02-15T19:08:02.882536Z",{"