"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/fc3a8d06a7787ef28c7a214bd773874796a392d2.png","Spruce Creeper","2025-02-15T19:07:08.964434Z",{"url":32046,"raw_url":32047,"featured":439,"title":32048,"description":3592,"created":32049,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/fe51a139f124f5e3a437b67267b7f2e6b59e53c2_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/fe51a139f124f5e3a437b67267b7f2e6b59e53c2.png","Alternating","2025-01-25T19:14:28.820036Z",{"url":32051,"raw_url":32052,"featured":439,"title":32053,"description":31967,"created":32054,"ordering":29981},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/a34d8696f9e753e81dccb3b8117484a5b079506f_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/a34d8696f9e753e81dccb3b8117484a5b079506f.png","Title Banner","2025-01-25T00:59:17.183662Z",{"url":32056,"raw_url":32057,"featured":439,"title":32058,"description":32059,"created":32060,"ordering":29981},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/f2186196f23e4d8fe0bc8d3601e3399831773761_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3KUxXJT/images/f2186196f23e4d8fe0bc8d3601e3399831773761.png","Some Creeper Variants","A selection of Creeper variants","2025-01-25T04:55:37.612338Z",2172176,"g5tMKFQX",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":32064,"id":32065,"slug":32066,"project_type":31,"team":32067,"organization":3592,"title":32068,"description":32069,"body":32070,"body_url":3592,"published":32071,"updated":32072,"approved":32073,"queued":32074,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":32075,"downloads":32076,"followers":29993,"categories":32077,"additional_categories":32078,"loaders":32079,"versions":32080,"icon_url":32084,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":32085,"gallery":32086,"color":32096,"thread_id":32097,"monetization_status":30002},[1271,1097,1043],"T4BZyj0Y","breaker-block","oIYCZqFM","Breaker Block","The Breaker Block breaks blocking blocks","The Breaker Block breaks blocks below it whenever it's activated by redstone,. The block can be pushed by pistons and can stick to Slime and Honey blocks.\n\nWhenever it breaks a block, it'll drop the item as if the player broke it (Stone into Cobblestone, for example) and the dropped item will be where the block originally was.\n\nThis mod is free to use in any modpack, provided that you include proper credits.","2023-11-03T10:13:17.302126Z","2024-03-16T15:48:40.833459Z","2023-11-05T02:07:42.921784Z","2023-11-03T10:19:17.692377Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},878,[288],[],[354],[32081,32082,32083],"vKx3v5EV","6Abyj0HD","mnlwWXSr","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4BZyj0Y/db0e0d1b8dbca5040843eecba1a6432ffd7c2160_96.webp",[],[32087,32091],{"url":32088,"raw_url":32088,"featured":849,"title":32068,"description":32089,"created":32090,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4BZyj0Y/images/a6d25988797597fd4759ec5cee446abd30684db8.png","The look of the breaker block","2023-11-03T10:16:23.630283Z",{"url":32092,"raw_url":32092,"featured":439,"title":32093,"description":32094,"created":32095,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4BZyj0Y/images/e178e03a356b85385580bc8fd6aa41d42a46f1aa.png","Crafting Recipie","The crafting recipie for the Breaker Block","2023-11-03T10:16:13.336089Z",4079166,"dJCkfHnS",{"client_side":30037,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":32099,"id":32100,"slug":32101,"project_type":31,"team":32102,"organization":3592,"title":32103,"description":32104,"body":32105,"body_url":3592,"published":32106,"updated":32107,"approved":32108,"queued":32109,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":32110,"downloads":32111,"followers":32112,"categories":32113,"additional_categories":32114,"loaders":32115,"versions":32116,"icon_url":32158,"issues_url":32159,"source_url":32160,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":32161,"gallery":32164,"color":32165,"thread_id":32166,"monetization_status":30002},[1172,1043,1010,968,962,890,884,847,841,793,790,760,712,670,661,655,610,604,559,505,499,487],"T3yW5Gzn","ore-discovery-broadcast","aIiuWClT","Ore Discovery Broadcast","⛏️ Broadcasts a message to the server whenever a player finds an ore vein.","\u003Cp style=\"text-align:center\">\u003Ca href=\"https://serilum.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://cdn.serilum.com/description/header/header.png\" alt=\"A Serilum Mod. Made with love. Lots of active mods for Fabric, Forge and Neo!\" width=\"838\" height=\"400\">\u003C/a>\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align:center\">\u003Ca href=\"https://curseforge.com/members/serilum/projects\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://workflow.serilum.com/badges/svg/curseforge.svg&w=400\" alt=\"CurseForge\" width=\"200\">\u003C/a> \u003Ca href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Serilum\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://workflow.serilum.com/badges/svg/modrinth.svg&w=400\" alt=\"Modrinth\" width=\"200\">\u003C/a> \u003Ca href=\"https://patreon.com/serilum\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://workflow.serilum.com/badges/svg/patreon.svg&w=400\" alt=\"Patreon\" width=\"200\">\u003C/a> \u003Ca href=\"https://youtube.com/@serilum\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://workflow.serilum.com/badges/svg/youtube.svg&w=400\" alt=\"YouTube\" width=\"200\">\u003C/a>\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align:center\">\u003Cbr>\u003Cimg src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/nameplate/about-the-mod.svg&w=1676\" alt=\"About the mod\" width=\"838\" height=\"64\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:18px\">Ore Discovery Broadcast is a mod made specifically for server environments, but can still be used in singleplayer or LAN worlds. Whenever a player mines an ore, a message is broadcasted. With a configurable delay in between messages from the same ore. The format and colour of the message can be changed. It's also possible to choose which ores should be broadcasted, and which shouldn't, via the blacklist file.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>Allows for more interaction between players, seeing what others are doing and which ores they find. The mod is also a viable solution as xray-prevention. As it's very noticable when a player keeps finding diamonds in an unnatural way. By default, the functionality is only enabled in dedicated servers. Can be changed by setting '\u003Cem>\u003Cstrong>onlyRunOnDedicatedServers\u003C/strong>\u003C/em>' in the config to \u003Cem>\u003Cstrong>false\u003C/strong>\u003C/em>. Placed ore blocks by players will not be broadcasted.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align:center\">\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cimg src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/nameplate/dependencies.svg&w=1676\" alt=\"Dependencies\" width=\"838\" height=\"64\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Ca href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/collective\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/badges/dependencies/requires/collective.svg&w=502\" alt=\"Requires Collective\" width=\"251\" height=\"49\">\u003C/a>\u003Cbr>\u003Cimg src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/badges/environment/server.svg&w=440\" alt=\"Environment: Server\" width=\"220\" height=\"49\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align:center\">\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cimg src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/nameplate/configurable.svg&w=1676\" alt=\"Configurable\" width=\"838\" height=\"64\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Ca href=\"https://serilum.com/configuration-guide\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/badges/configuration-guide.svg&w=440\" alt=\"Configuration guide\" width=\"220\" height=\"49\">\u003C/a>\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cp>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:18px\">All available config options:\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cdetails>\u003Csummary>Show Spoiler\u003C/summary>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">\u003Cstrong>onlyRunOnDedicatedServers\u003C/strong>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8a8d91\">&nbsp;&nbsp;default true\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:13px\">If the mod should only run on dedicated servers. When enabled it's not sent when in a singleplayer world.\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">\u003Cstrong>ignorePlacedOreBlocks\u003C/strong>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8a8d91\">&nbsp;&nbsp;default true\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:13px\">If ore blocks placed by players should be ignored for broadcasts.\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">\u003Cstrong>tickDelayBetweenSameOreBroastcasts\u003C/strong>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8a8d91\">&nbsp;&nbsp;default 600, min 0, max 72000\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:13px\">How many ticks in between ore discoveries before another broadcast is sent. Resets when the same block is mined. 20 ticks = 1 second\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">\u003Cstrong>messageFormat\u003C/strong>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8a8d91\">&nbsp;&nbsp;default \"%player% has found %ore%!\"\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:13px\">The format of the broadcasted message. %player% = player name, %ore% = ore name\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">\u003Cstrong>lowercaseOreName\u003C/strong>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8a8d91\">&nbsp;&nbsp;default true\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:13px\">Whether the ore name should be displayed in lowercase characters.\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">\u003Cstrong>addOreCountToMessage\u003C/strong>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8a8d91\">&nbsp;&nbsp;default false\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:13px\">If the broadcasted message should contain how big the ore vein is. Will be included in %ore%.\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">\u003Cstrong>hideDeepslateFromName\u003C/strong>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8a8d91\">&nbsp;&nbsp;default true\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:13px\">Whether the ore name should have 'deepslate' hidden if it exists.\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">\u003Cstrong>ignoreCreativePlayers\u003C/strong>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8a8d91\">&nbsp;&nbsp;default true\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:13px\">If enabled, ore discoveries won't be announced when a player is in creative mode.\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">\u003Cstrong>ignoreFakePlayers\u003C/strong>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8a8d91\">&nbsp;&nbsp;default true\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:13px\">If enabled, ore discoveries won't be announced when it is broken by a simulated fake player.\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:24px\">\u003Cstrong>Ore Blacklist\u003C/strong>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">There is a \u003Cem>\u003Cstrong>blacklist.txt\u003C/strong>\u003C/em> file available in the folder \u003Cem>\u003Cstrong>./config/orediscoverybroadcast/\u003C/strong>\u003C/em>. Here you can specify which ores shouldn't be broadcasted when found, by adding an exclamation mark (!) in front of the line. Quartz is excluded by default:\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cimg src=\"https://cdn.serilum.com/projects/ore-discovery-broadcast/a.png\" alt=\"\">\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:24px\">\u003Cstrong>Broadcast message colour config\u003C/strong>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">Inside \u003Cem>\u003Cstrong>./config/orediscoverybroadcast/.\u003C/strong>\u003C/em> there is also a file called \u003Cem>\u003Cstrong>colourmap.txt\u003C/strong>\u003C/em>. Here you can specify what colour should be set for specific ores. Contains default values.\u003Cbr>Ores from other mods will also be shown, with the default colour blue (9):\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cimg src=\"https://cdn.serilum.com/projects/ore-discovery-broadcast/a1.png\" alt=\"\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003C/details>\r\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align:center\">\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cimg src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/nameplate/showcase.svg&w=1676\" alt=\"Showcase\" width=\"838\" height=\"64\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">Here you can see the message being broadcast to the server. Mining multiple of the same ores only shows one message. Mining different ores shows multiple:\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cdetails>\u003Csummary>Show Spoiler\u003C/summary>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"https://cdn.serilum.com/projects/ore-discovery-broadcast/b.webp\" alt=\"\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003C/details>\r\n\u003Cp>&nbsp;\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">Another example with mining multiple coal ore:\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cdetails>\u003Csummary>Show Spoiler\u003C/summary>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"https://cdn.serilum.com/projects/ore-discovery-broadcast/c.webp\" alt=\"\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003C/details>\r\n\u003Cp>&nbsp;\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">Here the message format has been changed in the config. The content and colour is configurable:\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cdetails>\u003Csummary>Show Spoiler\u003C/summary>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"https://cdn.serilum.com/projects/ore-discovery-broadcast/d.webp\" alt=\"\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003C/details>\r\n\u003Cp>&nbsp;\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">A different colour can be set for each ore:\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cdetails>\u003Csummary>Show Spoiler\u003C/summary>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"https://cdn.serilum.com/projects/ore-discovery-broadcast/g.webp\" alt=\"\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003C/details>\r\n\u003Cp>&nbsp;\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">Here's an example with the '\u003Cstrong>\u003Cem>addOreCountToMessage\u003C/em>\u003C/strong>' config option enabled. The broadcasted message will contain how many ores are included in the vein:\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cdetails>\u003Csummary>Show Spoiler\u003C/summary>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"https://cdn.serilum.com/projects/ore-discovery-broadcast/f.webp\" alt=\"\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003C/details>\r\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align:center\">\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cimg src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://cdn.serilum.com/description/nameplate/notes-n-links.svg&w=1676\" alt=\"Notes and links\" width=\"838\" height=\"64\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:24px\">\u003Cstrong>You may freely use this mod in any modpack, as long as the download remains hosted within the CurseForge or Modrinth ecosystem.\u003C/strong>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:18px\">\u003Ca style=\"font-size:18px;color:#008000\" href=\"https://serilum.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Serilum.com\u003C/a> contains an overview and more information on all mods available.\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:14px\">\u003Cbr>For issues, ideas, suggestions or anything else there is the&nbsp;\u003Ca style=\"font-size:14px;color:#008000\" href=\"https://github.com/Serilum/.issue-tracker\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Github repo\u003C/a>. Thanks!\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"font-size:6px\">\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003C/span>\u003C/p>","2023-12-05T10:19:27.552884Z","2026-05-01T21:30:46.234944Z","2023-12-06T07:34:21.640891Z","2023-12-05T10:24:25.813294Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},19856,19,[30,275],[],[346,354,385,409],[32117,32118,32119,32120,32121,32122,32123,32124,32125,32126,32127,32128,32129,32130,32131,32132,32133,32134,32135,32136,32137,32138,32139,32140,32141,32142,32143,32144,32145,32146,32147,32148,32149,32150,32151,32152,32153,32154,32155,32156,32157],"d2r2rkZz","evD342ew","K7wShrNq","nyFCKZk1","TiSOwprI","tyYzgXpb","Iq4u4zQi","rjeiaOPw","QuByhW4l","H9jnkE57","xU2YG0p0","heQOra6w","WXUD95AW","rIrxaAtp","g40cBEAl","KuyKMVIh","dlJRZlvc","440zkWEi","BBNNgm2i","DDbboeK0","xod55CnK","HmgI0DsR","yiV8cMlu","iLuLZKGw","po84IHyH","pArgghTZ","q43yC7gy","dXErsPvw","mMsyFk1S","z7yvBmVY","JyVvX7nz","aWwd1b43","jxwl9Fpw","EhX2kiOy","rrG6PxMd","Ug9TMDwv","F7Ic5ll1","2Dp9XVVk","ApaJLNMR","G5xCEhqv","SkKOyQxE","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3yW5Gzn/060bb564a48248d44c385c0de622488d9390b47d_96.webp","https://github.com/Serilum/.issue-tracker/labels/Mod: Ore Discovery Broadcast","https://github.com/Serilum/Ore-Discovery-Broadcast",[32162],{"id":3137,"platform":3138,"url":32163},"https://patreon.com/serilum",[],6052699,"CePeutso",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":32168,"id":32169,"slug":32170,"project_type":31,"team":32171,"organization":3592,"title":32172,"description":32173,"body":32174,"body_url":3592,"published":32175,"updated":32176,"approved":32177,"queued":32178,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":32179,"downloads":30409,"followers":30075,"categories":32180,"additional_categories":32181,"loaders":32182,"versions":32183,"icon_url":3592,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":32185,"gallery":32186,"color":3592,"thread_id":32204,"monetization_status":30002},[841],"T45GLQqC","shadows-custom-cobblemon-pack","iMgLS12O","Shadow's Custom Cobblemon Pack","This mod adds 5 custom gym badges for the server I play on.","This mod adds 5 badges that me and my friends can use in our server. This mod was made fully for our server but feel free to download and check it out. The badges were made between us so they do vary in detail.\n\nBadges include:\n\nVenomheart Valor = Fighting, Fairy and Poison badge (designed by ShadowKnight666).\nHalocharge = Normal, Electric, Flying (designed by Potato_Engineer).\nPyrocore = Fire, Rock, Ground (designed by KermitTheFrog).\nEclipseshade Sigil = Psychic, Dark, Ghost (designed by Sensei).\nFrostscale = Ice, Steel, Dragon (designed by ShadowKnight666).\n\n\nThere will be more coming to this mod soon, with the badges being able to give you effects when held in the offhand.","2026-05-16T17:32:26.842765Z","2026-05-16T17:52:17.566190Z","2026-05-19T01:22:27.803459Z","2026-05-16T18:34:05.987051Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},[30,275,303],[],[385],[32184],"BPIH3LoN",[],[32187,32191,32195,32199],{"url":32188,"raw_url":32188,"featured":439,"title":32189,"description":3592,"created":32190,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T45GLQqC/images/027fef447048b8f32eefa42931b068b22781d23a.png","Pyrocore Badge","2026-05-16T18:23:24.393774Z",{"url":32192,"raw_url":32192,"featured":439,"title":32193,"description":3592,"created":32194,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T45GLQqC/images/68c93635512895528a40ca55da856f56ab62539d.png","Halocharge Badge","2026-05-16T18:22:37.890830Z",{"url":32196,"raw_url":32196,"featured":439,"title":32197,"description":3592,"created":32198,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T45GLQqC/images/9b13051c5ea7386d173e12197bf1be70fd4efe31.png","Eclipseshade Sigil Badge","2026-05-16T18:23:55.168137Z",{"url":32200,"raw_url":32201,"featured":439,"title":32202,"description":3592,"created":32203,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T45GLQqC/images/b6057b1b6451d63d649305c5cc5dc5ca76febe20_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T45GLQqC/images/b6057b1b6451d63d649305c5cc5dc5ca76febe20.png","Venomheart Valor Badge","2026-05-16T18:20:26.895903Z","69mmQtq4",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":32206,"id":32207,"slug":32208,"project_type":31,"team":32209,"organization":3592,"title":32210,"description":32211,"body":32212,"body_url":3592,"published":32213,"updated":32214,"approved":32215,"queued":32216,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":32217,"downloads":32218,"followers":29999,"categories":32219,"additional_categories":32220,"loaders":32221,"versions":32222,"icon_url":32234,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":32235,"gallery":32236,"color":31246,"thread_id":32249,"monetization_status":30002},[841],"T33ScMoh","irs","YBNY9uCl","IRS","The IRS is haunting us... help...","This is a horror mod… about paying your taxes.\n\nI don’t know anymore. They won’t leave me alone. They never will…\n\n![The Papers.](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/fd268ae2e482532a428a8fd66924baa12585cb85_0.webp)\n\nThe IRS adds a few absolutely TERRIFYING and HORRIFYING entities to Minecraft, like the Tax Collector, who comes for you if you don’t pay your taxes within one in-game day. Ignore them… and face the consequences.\n\n!! Headphones strongly recommended for the full experience !!\n\nWhy play this mod?\n\n- Because evading your taxes fun.\n\n- Because nothing in Minecraft has ever made you feel this amount of fear.\n\n- Because Pablo loves you.\n\nWarning:\n\n- Very early in development--bugs are expected.\n\n- This is for entertainment only; don’t try tax evasion in real life.\n\n- Pay your taxes, or… don’t, but know the consequences are coming.","2025-08-28T01:16:35.629345Z","2026-04-03T23:24:31.197660Z","2025-09-08T03:14:18.561442Z","2025-09-06T19:27:00.374705Z",{"id":30051,"name":10,"url":3592},495,[93,134,191],[30,105,316],[385],[32223,32224,32225,32226,32227,32228,32229,32230,32231,32232,32233],"HCXuGFke","kOBSvm0s","wnKRiH61","xBmo7qkS","ONNgeHRB","xUoms1hH","wDTM8Met","ZamQVAsP","1JfDvfIz","LOKwfKiS","GFGSJR5g","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T33ScMoh/1b9a8ea121c24c559ab11a834e0056c9864995e7_96.webp",[],[32237,32243],{"url":32238,"raw_url":32239,"featured":439,"title":32240,"description":32241,"created":32242,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T33ScMoh/images/0f65dd849681eab364bcb9e0c6ba0ec40b7a9765_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T33ScMoh/images/0f65dd849681eab364bcb9e0c6ba0ec40b7a9765.png","i love cats ",":)","2025-09-04T23:46:09.622030Z",{"url":32244,"raw_url":32245,"featured":439,"title":32246,"description":32247,"created":32248,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T33ScMoh/images/2419362404e1a36f50ad9f7d736d4896ed6976ca_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T33ScMoh/images/2419362404e1a36f50ad9f7d736d4896ed6976ca.png","Himself.","The \"man\" himself.","2025-08-31T00:32:55.861740Z","iD6RmNDw",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":32251,"id":32252,"slug":32253,"project_type":31,"team":32254,"organization":3592,"title":32255,"description":32256,"body":32257,"body_url":3592,"published":32258,"updated":32259,"approved":32260,"queued":32261,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":32262,"downloads":32263,"followers":29987,"categories":32264,"additional_categories":32265,"loaders":32266,"versions":32267,"icon_url":32269,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":32270,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":32271,"gallery":32272,"color":32298,"thread_id":32299,"monetization_status":30002},[1010],"T33E9SFz","arrowblockdeployer","UfBaSHtD","ArrowBlockDeployer","Introducing the ArrowBlockDeployer mod! This handy mod features the Block Launcher Bow, a unique item that lets you place blocks from a distance.","Introducing the ArrowBlockDeployer mod! This handy mod features the Block Launcher Bow, a unique item that lets you place blocks from a distance. With four distinct types of arrows, you can enhance your gameplay in useful ways:\n\nGlow Berry Attached Arrow - Perfect for illuminating ceilings.\nGlowing Dirt Attached Arrow - Versatile lighting for ceilings, underwater areas, and anywhere else you need.\nTNT Attached Arrow - Place TNT blocks remotely (requires separate activation).\nTorch Attached Arrow - Cost-effective solution for lighting up distant areas.\nWhether you're lighting up ceilings, underwater areas, or setting up remote explosives, the ArrowBlockDeployer mod is designed to support your Minecraft adventures. Enjoy a new level of convenience and creativity with the Block Launcher Bow!\n\n\nこのModでは、ブロック射出弓という弓と、四種のカスタム矢によって、ブロックを遠隔で配置することができます。 矢の種類は以下の通りです。\n\nグロウベリー付きの矢 - 天井を明るくするのに最適です。\n発光する土付きの矢 - 天井、水中など、どこでも汎用的に明るくできます。\nTNT付きの矢 - TNTを遠隔で置くことができます（起爆は別途必要）。\n松明付きの矢 - 低コストで遠くを明るくしたいときに最適です。\nバニラでは明るくしづらい天井や水中を、簡単に明るくすることができます。 暗いところが苦手な方におすすめです。","2025-04-20T21:56:50.845541Z","2025-04-20T22:10:43.636391Z","2025-04-24T06:25:03.899353Z","2025-04-20T22:13:13.572626Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},49,[303],[],[354],[32268],"uP3o2Qzf","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T33E9SFz/f354b5f7ad19387fbdc2f2ad0f384775eafe9ec7.png","https://github.com/oimogenius/ArrowBlockDeployer",[],[32273,32278,32283,32288,32293],{"url":32274,"raw_url":32275,"featured":439,"title":32276,"description":3592,"created":32277,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T33E9SFz/images/95c7e6e460c9c512116adeecfd12e06e665b48bd_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T33E9SFz/images/95c7e6e460c9c512116adeecfd12e06e665b48bd.png","Creative Tab","2025-04-20T22:06:13.871586Z",{"url":32279,"raw_url":32280,"featured":439,"title":32281,"description":3592,"created":32282,"ordering":29981},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T33E9SFz/images/f909443c716b79316904209a96b87aab3c6abb58_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T33E9SFz/images/f909443c716b79316904209a96b87aab3c6abb58.png","Bow Recipe","2025-04-20T22:06:51.440373Z",{"url":32284,"raw_url":32285,"featured":439,"title":32286,"description":3592,"created":32287,"ordering":29987},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T33E9SFz/images/51facf0e9fb1f16a481ddd0cdfe684f821cdc8a1_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T33E9SFz/images/51facf0e9fb1f16a481ddd0cdfe684f821cdc8a1.png","Glowberry Attached Arrow","2025-04-20T22:07:16.097835Z",{"url":32289,"raw_url":32290,"featured":439,"title":32291,"description":3592,"created":32292,"ordering":29993},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T33E9SFz/images/0d5c5f8d8740bc611d65bb009bdaf809c50e130d_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T33E9SFz/images/0d5c5f8d8740bc611d65bb009bdaf809c50e130d.png","Glowing Dirt","2025-04-20T22:07:41.927002Z",{"url":32294,"raw_url":32295,"featured":439,"title":32296,"description":3592,"created":32297,"ordering":29999},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T33E9SFz/images/2431dda1b112c18650b85ec77e9beebb31d0dc5c_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T33E9SFz/images/2431dda1b112c18650b85ec77e9beebb31d0dc5c.png","Placed Glowing Dirt","2025-04-20T22:08:11.211319Z",4473924,"R5GIYr5L",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":32301,"id":32302,"slug":32303,"project_type":31,"team":32304,"organization":3592,"title":32305,"description":32306,"body":32307,"body_url":3592,"published":32308,"updated":32309,"approved":32310,"queued":32311,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":32312,"downloads":32313,"followers":29993,"categories":32314,"additional_categories":32315,"loaders":32316,"versions":32317,"icon_url":32322,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":32323,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":32324,"gallery":32325,"color":32332,"thread_id":32333,"monetization_status":30002},[760],"T37ZT2r7","hardness-patch","y08HHwui","Hardness Patch","Allows users to adjust the hardness values of all blocks (modded and vanilla) using their block ID and a float value.","Allows users to adjust the hardness values of *all* blocks (modded and vanilla) using their block ID and a float value.\n\n**THIS MOD MUST BE ON BOTH THE SERVER AND THE CLIENT!**\n\nUses a convenient configuration screen using Cloth Config API. Alternatively, you can edit `hardnesspatch.json5`.\n\nChanges made to the config should apply immediately without reloading the world/game.\nRequires [Cloth Config API](https://modrinth.com/mod/cloth-config) and [Mod Menu](https://modrinth.com/mod/modmenu)\n\nThis mod does not seem to work properly in [Essential](https://modrinth.com/mod/essential) multiplayer. Hopefully I can fix this sometime soon.","2025-02-16T01:32:16.196506Z","2025-02-16T21:34:01.155928Z","2025-02-17T10:20:08.441Z","2025-02-16T10:14:30.665557Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},406,[134,175,303],[],[346],[32318,32319,32320,32321],"7jl4QQCl","XdL0rXNh","WpQidKpU","pZjvN9yO","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T37ZT2r7/c6aa82f1bde4845baa24ebaf6c4283d3ea629b79.png","https://github.com/pinexd/Hardness-Patch",[],[32326],{"url":32327,"raw_url":32328,"featured":849,"title":32329,"description":32330,"created":32331,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T37ZT2r7/images/7026b5de46a40864867e8e54e644b604fb65efd9_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T37ZT2r7/images/7026b5de46a40864867e8e54e644b604fb65efd9.png","Config screen","+ to add a block. Name it, then save and it will be added to the list. To remove an entry, toggle the removal button, and save.","2025-02-16T01:42:02.135338Z",11184810,"HuhOTs54",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":32335,"id":32336,"slug":32337,"project_type":31,"team":32338,"organization":3592,"title":32339,"description":32340,"body":32341,"body_url":3592,"published":32342,"updated":32343,"approved":32344,"queued":32345,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":32346,"downloads":31162,"followers":29981,"categories":32347,"additional_categories":32348,"loaders":32349,"versions":32350,"icon_url":32352,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":32353,"gallery":32356,"color":32403,"thread_id":32404,"monetization_status":30002},[1172],"T4NkD2rb","more_tree_sizes","ylSB94es","More_Tree_Sizes","Adds more vanilla trees to your world in different sizes to help spice up your landscape while keeping the game vanilla friendly.","I made this mod becasue I just wanted a simple mod that would add a little more tree variety to my game without needing to install a major mod that required constant updating or complex api dependencies.  This is just a simple mod that adds trees. Oddly, this didn't seem to exist as many of the tree mods were overly complex, or completly changed minecraft trees and biomes.  This one does not do that. It is a No Fuss tree mod that just adds in a few tree sizes. It does not alter existing vanilla trees.\n\nThis is a simple vanilla friendly mod that adds three new tree sizes to your world: Medium, Large and Huge.\n\nThese trees will spawn sporadically in their respective biomes, blending into the landscape, yet adding some variety to the trees and skyline of your game. Cherry trees in the cherry biome, birch trees in the birch forest biomes, Acacia trees in Savannah biomes, etc... (Note, version 1.19.2 wont include cherry trees.)\n\nThe large trees are about twice the size of normal trees, and the huge trees are about 4 to 5 times as large and are rare, but beautiful to behold and could serve as excellent base locations or the source of a lot of wood.\n\nDue to the size of the huge tree canopy, mobs may spawn naturally under/in them during the day, but if you've ever cliimbed a real tree, then you know spiders are a pretty common occurance in the real world.\n\nThis mod does not have any dependencies.\n\nDid I mention this mod is simple and just adds trees?\n\nCurerntly available on forge 1.19.2 , 1.20.1 and NeoForge1.21.1\n\nYes, you may include this in your modpack.","2025-05-09T00:30:42.286822Z","2025-05-09T00:31:01.590272Z","2025-05-11T05:08:53.873077Z","2025-05-09T00:39:55.618886Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},[30,316],[],[354],[32351],"9JvaWrcE","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/ce825164c22f3acc7c831cf2673552029266ff70_96.webp",[32354],{"id":3152,"platform":3153,"url":32355},"https://earthartgems.com/",[32357,32362,32367,32373,32378,32383,32388,32393,32398],{"url":32358,"raw_url":32359,"featured":439,"title":32360,"description":3592,"created":32361,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/08b8c0ffc71ba390063a5fd19e31e904aba58a9d_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/08b8c0ffc71ba390063a5fd19e31e904aba58a9d.jpeg","Adds larger mushrooms!","2025-05-09T00:39:31.408770Z",{"url":32363,"raw_url":32364,"featured":439,"title":32365,"description":3592,"created":32366,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/1e65c76adf77598ac8796b16cf06bfc0ae115d68_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/1e65c76adf77598ac8796b16cf06bfc0ae115d68.jpeg","Looking at a huge spruce","2025-05-09T00:39:06.228648Z",{"url":32368,"raw_url":32369,"featured":849,"title":32370,"description":32371,"created":32372,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/2047426afbed1a6574a610d62390fa92a86abf2f_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/2047426afbed1a6574a610d62390fa92a86abf2f.jpeg","Large Oak","Seamless ground generation","2025-05-09T00:37:16.214985Z",{"url":32374,"raw_url":32375,"featured":439,"title":32376,"description":3592,"created":32377,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/29f65d6da71da3777db4b0008f57a4a378a7d72a_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/29f65d6da71da3777db4b0008f57a4a378a7d72a.jpeg","Added a new Cactus","2025-05-09T00:36:17.737691Z",{"url":32379,"raw_url":32380,"featured":439,"title":32381,"description":3592,"created":32382,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/3a5b93b0946f6b33266759b5ecb402705eb81700_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/3a5b93b0946f6b33266759b5ecb402705eb81700.jpeg","Huge Acacia Tree Variant","2025-05-09T00:38:18.895718Z",{"url":32384,"raw_url":32385,"featured":439,"title":32386,"description":3592,"created":32387,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/84fc2a5f3567937abe914f65c3765d56a0bd9406_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/84fc2a5f3567937abe914f65c3765d56a0bd9406.jpeg","A medium Dark Oak","2025-05-09T00:36:45.496533Z",{"url":32389,"raw_url":32390,"featured":439,"title":32391,"description":3592,"created":32392,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/a97914774755fbfc88cf240c1fe7eaecfcb60141_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/a97914774755fbfc88cf240c1fe7eaecfcb60141.jpeg","Large Cherry Tree","2025-05-09T00:35:50.162306Z",{"url":32394,"raw_url":32395,"featured":439,"title":32396,"description":3592,"created":32397,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/c35b02c080b6bf4ab232aa690b42abafa74fafd4_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/c35b02c080b6bf4ab232aa690b42abafa74fafd4.jpeg","medium sized acacia tree","2025-05-09T00:35:25.270526Z",{"url":32399,"raw_url":32400,"featured":439,"title":32401,"description":3592,"created":32402,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/fa6fbaa6a517e2479a4c2af0dad1ce08e138dae0_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T4NkD2rb/images/fa6fbaa6a517e2479a4c2af0dad1ce08e138dae0.jpeg","Large Swamp Oak","2025-05-09T00:37:41.602920Z",2301715,"a8ET5U4B",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":32406,"id":32407,"slug":32408,"project_type":31,"team":32409,"organization":3592,"title":32410,"description":32411,"body":32412,"body_url":3592,"published":32413,"updated":32414,"approved":32415,"queued":32416,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":32417,"downloads":32419,"followers":29999,"categories":32420,"additional_categories":32421,"loaders":32422,"versions":32423,"icon_url":32429,"issues_url":32430,"source_url":32431,"wiki_url":32432,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":32433,"gallery":32434,"color":32451,"thread_id":32452,"monetization_status":30002},[1043],"T3kp7qzA","rock-your-socks-off","TIv6oTPN","Rock Your Socks Off","Adds a whole bunch of socks to your game. Each pair of socks give you a special effect.","![RYSO logo](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8ef875ccc82f3bbcd81c65e05bdcb090c5f3f206.png)\n\nThis is a silly mod about a whole bunch of colorful socks with varying magical abilities that range from simple buffs to powerful new abilities.\nMake socks to fight tooth and nail, make socks to befriend unlikely allies or make socks to look snazzy! It's all up to you what you do with these powerful pieces of footware.\n\nFor the best experience possible, the Trinkets API is strongly recommended, as it adds a new slot for the socks to go in without taking up the boots slot. However it is not required to run the mod.\n\nCurrently RYSO has 18 pairs of socks:\n- Blank socks\n- Light grey socks\n- Grey socks\n- Black socks\n- Brown socks\n- Red socks\n- Orange socks\n- Yellow socks\n- Lime socks\n- Green socks\n- Cyan socks\n- Light blue socks\n- Blue socks\n- Purple socks\n- Magenta socks\n- Pink socks\n- Rainbow socks\n- Jolly socks","2025-06-04T21:46:14.109175Z","2026-04-29T20:11:58.525717Z","2025-06-19T21:32:34.888458Z","2025-06-11T23:40:13.609348Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":32418},"https://github.com/oathompsonjones/rock-your-socks-off/blob/main/LICENSE",295,[115],[30,171],[346],[32424,32425,32426,32427,32428],"ew4Baukw","gTj91iOf","YdO3m5cj","HBdvBNIX","tbN7m1jg","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3kp7qzA/c0296f8bbe139460fe097547491074e577c2ee79.png","https://github.com/oathompsonjones/rock-your-socks-off/issues","https://github.com/oathompsonjones/rock-your-socks-off","https://github.com/oathompsonjones/rock-your-socks-off/wiki",[],[32435,32439,32445],{"url":32436,"raw_url":32437,"featured":439,"title":32410,"description":3592,"created":32438,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3kp7qzA/images/5dd5e9e4653ac18d8d45c7bb5b743abaf8d5b937_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3kp7qzA/images/5dd5e9e4653ac18d8d45c7bb5b743abaf8d5b937.png","2025-06-04T21:54:35.552747Z",{"url":32440,"raw_url":32441,"featured":439,"title":32442,"description":32443,"created":32444,"ordering":29981},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3kp7qzA/images/6e12e7e53da2cec3b49debb0968ee5036791c8b2_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3kp7qzA/images/6e12e7e53da2cec3b49debb0968ee5036791c8b2.png","Crafting recipes 1.0","The crafting recipes for half of the socks in the mod.","2025-06-04T22:22:19.901012Z",{"url":32446,"raw_url":32447,"featured":439,"title":32448,"description":32449,"created":32450,"ordering":29987},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3kp7qzA/images/64f6c9586dcfdd405a5178bcd516381e1a3ce0fb_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3kp7qzA/images/64f6c9586dcfdd405a5178bcd516381e1a3ce0fb.png","Crafting recipes 1.0 ","The other half of the crafting recipes of RYSO.","2025-06-04T22:22:57.955122Z",3428927,"1cnosCSu",{"client_side":29949,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":32454,"id":32455,"slug":32456,"project_type":31,"team":32457,"organization":3592,"title":32458,"description":32459,"body":32460,"body_url":3592,"published":32461,"updated":32462,"approved":32463,"queued":32464,"status":29937,"requested_status":29939,"moderator_message":3592,"license":32465,"downloads":30366,"followers":29981,"categories":32466,"additional_categories":32467,"loaders":32468,"versions":32469,"icon_url":32472,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":32473,"gallery":32474,"color":32475,"thread_id":32476,"monetization_status":30002},[1049,1043],"T2yRWbuO","create-reatomized-caravans","IdrOyCSU","Create Reatomized: Pillager Caravans","A datapack for Obscuria's Pillager Caravans which replaces their Vanilla style caravans with a total of 90 new caravans which include many modded mobs.","A Datapack which adds caravans for Obscuria's Pillager Caravans mod. These Caravans include mobs from _Scorched Guns 2_, _Savage & Ravage_, _Raids:Enhanced_, _It Takes a Pillage_, and _Born in Chaos_. There are a total of 90 caravans that spawn across differing climates. Specifically made for compatibility with Biomes O' Plenty, Regions Unexplored, and Terralith. **Disable the default Pillager Caravans' \"Classic Caravans\" datapack before use.**","2026-05-02T09:53:29.483593Z","2026-05-24T07:53:50.459615Z","2026-05-25T02:11:59.195087Z","2026-05-24T07:54:32.373855Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},[134],[],[342],[32470,32471],"cUeFBome","bv41Pb8n","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRWbuO/d5a5585aadcb1ea4de41afd35e9ee1b180681ff9_96.webp",[],[],3812392,"gr1HGutv",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":32478,"id":32479,"slug":32480,"project_type":34,"team":32481,"organization":3592,"title":32482,"description":32483,"body":32484,"body_url":3592,"published":32485,"updated":32486,"approved":32487,"queued":32488,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":32489,"downloads":32490,"followers":29981,"categories":32491,"additional_categories":32492,"loaders":32493,"versions":32494,"icon_url":32499,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":32500,"donation_urls":32501,"gallery":32504,"color":32510,"thread_id":32511,"monetization_status":30002},[1043],"T3NGNcgr","cellakay-the-tech-world","5PTuBpzt","CellaKay - The Tech World","A pack for technical enthusiasts","A package created from players and for players!\n\n+---------------------------------------------+\n\nPacket includes technical and adventure aspects.\nIncluded among other modifications are:\n    - \"Applied Energistics\"\n    - \"Create\" with additions\n    - Custom modification \"CellaKay\" adding more novelties\n    - \"ComputerCraft\" with additions\n\n+---------------------------------------------+\n\nImmerse yourself in the world of ComputerCraft with the tasks! Open world, lots of friendships with machines. This is just CellaKay!\n\n+---------------------------------------------+\n\nPackage version: Alpha\nCreator: KayTech\nCreator links:\n    - https://kaytech.org/\n    - https://dsc.gg/kaytech","2024-08-06T13:42:12.028109Z","2024-08-30T12:26:34.224631Z","2024-08-09T05:10:40.775286Z","2024-08-08T12:20:27.311117Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":3592},188,[30,162,200],[288],[346],[32495,32496,32497,32498],"sToifl4A","CTOVCVO1","i2a2KcIp","ru5OSlLK","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3NGNcgr/d70a8b88d727cd3e7d563e4a72ff15d447a72a67_96.webp","https://dsc.gg/kaytech",[32502],{"id":3137,"platform":3138,"url":32503},"https://patreon.com/KayTechStudio",[32505],{"url":32506,"raw_url":32506,"featured":439,"title":32507,"description":32508,"created":32509,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3NGNcgr/images/5c10b9390f3df3bcf66dc3d3375be333f7548408.jpeg","Logo Paczki","Zawiera logo paczki","2024-08-06T13:52:06.992562Z",11053223,"Mww5a3kQ",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":29950,"game_versions":32513,"id":32514,"slug":32515,"project_type":31,"team":32516,"organization":3592,"title":32517,"description":32518,"body":32519,"body_url":3592,"published":32520,"updated":32521,"approved":32522,"queued":32523,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":32524,"downloads":32525,"followers":29981,"categories":32526,"additional_categories":32527,"loaders":32528,"versions":32529,"icon_url":32538,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":32539,"gallery":32543,"color":32602,"thread_id":32603,"monetization_status":30002},[1097,1043,962,884,841,760,655],"T2yRurhl","craftables-by-smplesco","n2t5FrpQ","Craftables by smplesco","Adds recipes to uncraftable vanilla items.","## Craft the uncraftable.\n![All New Craftables](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2547890682923558f8c6201c3748193c4a0771ac.jpeg)\nCurrent items include:\n\n- Leather/iron/gold/diamond horse armor\n- Enchanted golden apple\n- Totem of undying\n- Name tag\n- Bell\n- Glow ink sac\n- Packed/Blue ice\n- String\n- Trident\n  \nPlease comment on what else I should add.","2026-02-16T03:33:00.156785Z","2026-02-16T03:41:01.048642Z","2026-02-16T09:05:36.682280Z","2026-02-16T03:41:45.009891Z",{"id":30807,"name":30808,"url":3592},121,[100,115,303],[],[346,354,385],[32530,32531,32532,32533,32534,32535,32536,32537],"fGMZmO5q","hVPwYQeq","MSNTHTf3","pK9XF6ro","rh3wKJiJ","Qmwy5Fie","Xmzsve2F","TZVkSffK","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRurhl/f028331388a881c68a4b9a1937cdd6c638e102f8.png",[32540],{"id":3140,"platform":32541,"url":32542},"Bmac","https://buymeacoffee.com/smplesco",[32544,32549,32553,32557,32561,32565,32569,32574,32578,32582,32586,32590,32594,32598],{"url":32545,"raw_url":32546,"featured":849,"title":32547,"description":3592,"created":32548,"ordering":31002},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRurhl/images/47cb88aa76306e01ec4aa494782aacd07acde3bd_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRurhl/images/47cb88aa76306e01ec4aa494782aacd07acde3bd.png","All Craftable Items","2026-02-16T03:53:50.984579Z",{"url":32550,"raw_url":32550,"featured":439,"title":32551,"description":3592,"created":32552,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRurhl/images/2d096199973170c50a16f1e481e92ff339679ce3.png","Enchanted Golden Apple Recipe","2026-02-16T03:37:08.016119Z",{"url":32554,"raw_url":32554,"featured":439,"title":32555,"description":3592,"created":32556,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRurhl/images/3e7c73994555ab174059d3a654db0352b2deb3d6.png","Blue Ice Recipe","2026-02-16T03:36:00.928141Z",{"url":32558,"raw_url":32558,"featured":439,"title":32559,"description":3592,"created":32560,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRurhl/images/57ae4d2cf9ab172a7b8667d24d85bdb857ca26d1.png","Totem of Undying Recipe","2026-02-16T03:36:56.522283Z",{"url":32562,"raw_url":32562,"featured":439,"title":32563,"description":3592,"created":32564,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRurhl/images/7c83d46150bdb26651b6386ed101814cbe94dc06.png","Name Tag Recipe","2026-02-16T03:36:42.358043Z",{"url":32566,"raw_url":32566,"featured":439,"title":32567,"description":3592,"created":32568,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRurhl/images/8daa65a6930ba0728e86b8483fdba1b2da6414cc.png","Packed Ice Recipe","2026-02-16T03:36:11.094682Z",{"url":32570,"raw_url":32570,"featured":439,"title":32571,"description":32572,"created":32573,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRurhl/images/9362fcc538b186751b6f08a6bde19a7aa36f0b4c.png","String Recipe","Note: Any wool will return 4 string.","2026-02-16T03:35:29.731329Z",{"url":32575,"raw_url":32575,"featured":439,"title":32576,"description":3592,"created":32577,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRurhl/images/cc87e151bb6c3edf1ec6d04aad5042de04b9cab1.png","Glow Ink Sac Recipe","2026-02-16T03:36:21.795316Z",{"url":32579,"raw_url":32579,"featured":439,"title":32580,"description":3592,"created":32581,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRurhl/images/edf955be978a79d28f0cd2dc79bb4d3e9f64ebb7.png","Trident Recipe","2026-02-16T03:35:19.957923Z",{"url":32583,"raw_url":32583,"featured":439,"title":32584,"description":3592,"created":32585,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRurhl/images/fc2f05e779af24f17c69662233efdc53e36f8611.png","Bell Recipe","2026-02-16T03:36:30.567483Z",{"url":32587,"raw_url":32587,"featured":439,"title":32588,"description":3592,"created":32589,"ordering":29987},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRurhl/images/9c881793806987582f3ff6f70a8bfbe392c4a4c5.png","Leather Horse Armor Recipe","2026-02-16T03:59:18.331679Z",{"url":32591,"raw_url":32591,"featured":439,"title":32592,"description":3592,"created":32593,"ordering":29993},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRurhl/images/31fcd83ab4e2ba0b36fe6126cd03676265d09537.png","Iron Horse Armor Recipe","2026-02-16T03:59:28.640686Z",{"url":32595,"raw_url":32595,"featured":439,"title":32596,"description":3592,"created":32597,"ordering":29999},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRurhl/images/fdd50fe1fad49a3ac9a1f1baae5cb0f550a38e75.png","Gold Horse Armor Recipe","2026-02-16T03:59:40.466388Z",{"url":32599,"raw_url":32599,"featured":439,"title":32600,"description":3592,"created":32601,"ordering":30346},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T2yRurhl/images/725c29d782f2875ecddfbdcd94bba5eec6f90395.png","Diamond Horse Armor Recipe","2026-02-16T03:59:51.491947Z",6579300,"ZUPJE6lK",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":30037,"game_versions":32605,"id":32606,"slug":32607,"project_type":12,"team":32608,"organization":3592,"title":32609,"description":32610,"body":32611,"body_url":3592,"published":32612,"updated":32613,"approved":32614,"queued":32615,"status":29937,"requested_status":29937,"moderator_message":3592,"license":32616,"downloads":32619,"followers":30075,"categories":32620,"additional_categories":32621,"loaders":32622,"versions":32623,"icon_url":32625,"issues_url":3592,"source_url":3592,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":3592,"donation_urls":32626,"gallery":32627,"color":32632,"thread_id":32633,"monetization_status":30002},[1043],"T47axCaB","htp-oxidized-spanish-translation-pack","A07V4q6p","[HTP] Oxidized | Spanish Translation Pack","Unofficial spanish translation for the Oxidized mod. Includes all slangs/variations.","\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvb-uy/Hispanic-Translations-Project/f4f70024e4a8db7f38675822c37bd4cadfd73691/resources/banner.png\" alt=\"Banner\" width=\"1169\" height=\"301\" />\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">Spanish translations for the Oxidized mod.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">Supports all spanish variations / slangs.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">\u003Cstrong>How to install\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">1. Download the .zip file and put it inside the /resourcepacks folder inside .minecraft\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Choose the following language order, and put your preferred variation on the top\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvb-uy/Hispanic-Translations-Project/f4f70024e4a8db7f38675822c37bd4cadfd73691/resources/tutorial.png\" alt=\"Tutorial on how to select the languages for the pack to work\" width=\"617\" height=\"400\" />\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">\u003Cstrong>Who are we?\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">We're a small team with one simple goal: bring spanish translations to all mods as possible.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">Modded MC has a great chunk of spanish translated mods, but sadly, there's a lot more that aren't. There are also some cases where translations are inconsistent or incomplete.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">That's why we decided to make HTP, to try to fix this task.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">\u003Cstrong>Open Source\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">Our project is open source, contribution friendly, and most importantly,&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>under the Public Domain.\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">If you're a mod developer and want to add our translations officially to your mod, feel free to! We encourage it.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">These pages will still be updated frequently and serve as an unofficial translation, but the content of them is free to use for everyone.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">\u003Cstrong>Contributing\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">If you're a native spanish speaker and want to contribute by either adding more translations or proofreading, you can open a&nbsp;\u003Ca href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/pull-requests/collaborating-with-pull-requests/proposing-changes-to-your-work-with-pull-requests/creating-a-pull-request\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pull Request\u003C/a>&nbsp;in our&nbsp;\u003Ca href=\"https://github.com/nvb-uy/hispanic-translations-project\" rel=\"nofollow\">Github Repository\u003C/a>.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">\u003Cstrong>Donating\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">Your best donation is a contribution on our&nbsp;\u003Ca href=\"https://github.com/nvb-uy/hispanic-translations-project\" rel=\"nofollow\">Github Repository\u003C/a>!\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">If you don't want to open a pull request, you can always make an issue pointing out stuff to be improved on.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp style=\"text-align: center;\">Due to CurseForge moderation policies the description must be in english, the projects are not getting approved with spanish descriptions.\u003C/p>","2025-12-11T00:32:18.822847Z","2025-12-11T00:32:41.660463Z","2025-12-11T03:50:45.977868Z","2025-12-11T00:34:47.763599Z",{"id":32617,"name":32618,"url":3592},"CC0-1.0","Creative Commons Zero v1.0 Universal",318810,[],[],[377],[32624],"eWaQRr2L","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T47axCaB/7ee0e862a7d5313e56e686bc5761b2bd59460981_96.webp",[],[32628],{"url":32629,"raw_url":32629,"featured":439,"title":32630,"description":3592,"created":32631,"ordering":30075},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T47axCaB/images/ebb342f74e709e7a551b7f894addd2d144f830fe.png","Tutorial","2025-12-11T00:34:38.627864Z",3158320,"uc0V9f8F",{"client_side":29950,"server_side":30037,"game_versions":32635,"id":32636,"slug":32637,"project_type":31,"team":32638,"organization":3592,"title":32639,"description":32640,"body":32641,"body_url":3592,"published":32642,"updated":32643,"approved":32644,"queued":32645,"status":29937,"requested_status":29939,"moderator_message":3592,"license":32646,"downloads":32648,"followers":29993,"categories":32649,"additional_categories":32650,"loaders":32651,"versions":32652,"icon_url":32655,"issues_url":32656,"source_url":32657,"wiki_url":3592,"discord_url":32658,"donation_urls":32659,"gallery":32660,"color":32667,"thread_id":32668,"monetization_status":30002},[841],"T3HYc0tf","immersive-cave-ambience","1TjhRRO3","Immersive Cave Ambience","Enhance your cave ambience with skellies for ultimate spookiness","\u003Cp align=\"center\">\u003Ciframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/M85eHsghTcQ\" title=\"skeltal video\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen>\u003C/iframe>\n\u003C/p>\n\n![loaders: neoforge](https://img.shields.io/badge/NEOFORGE%20%7C%20FABRIC-ffffff?style=for-the-badge&label=LOADERS&labelColor=666d71&color=f2f7f7)   ![version: 1.21.1](https://img.shields.io/badge/1.21.1-ffffff?style=for-the-badge&label=VERSION&labelColor=666d71&color=f2f7f7)  \n\n## Immersive Cave Ambience:\n***\nIt's not October as of writing this (oh no), but we can still do a spooky thing. This mod makes a skeleton gif walk over the screen every time the scary vanilla ambient cave sound plays. If you put this in your friend's mod folder, they'll find out the fun way (evil), tho this is not really a screamer, just spooky.\n\u003Cbr>\n## Resourcepacks:\n***\nThis mod is technically resourcepackable. If you for some reason want to make one, you need to follow the [file structure](https://github.com/lethargistic/spooky/tree/1.21.1/common/src/main/resources) in the repo and make a spritesheet out of the gif/video frames.\n\n### Credits:\nA femur for [Aaron](https://aaronhowser.dev/) for the idea: \u003Cbr>  \u003Cimg width=\"48\" height=\"48\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f4c342c0f84c891c6c8221cef60d7d2181c6625a_0.webp\" alt=\"hand giving you a femur\">","2026-03-09T09:10:00.537145Z","2026-03-10T20:35:09.467652Z","2026-03-24T20:15:26.747997Z","2026-03-10T20:37:45.242287Z",{"id":29963,"name":29964,"url":32647},"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lethargistic/spooky/refs/heads/1.21.1/LICENSE",392,[93],[],[346,385],[32653,32654],"LgTEXefG","B9W7EshE","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3HYc0tf/15ad1d14edf94f28951ed725f899251c15b4af38_96.webp","https://github.com/lethargistic/spooky/issues","https://github.com/lethargistic/spooky","https://discord.gg/wjuXNBED6x",[],[32661],{"url":32662,"raw_url":32663,"featured":849,"title":32664,"description":32665,"created":32666,"ordering":29981},"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3HYc0tf/images/eccd047472667c5ef520a8ae60d88fea76d07ab8_350.webp","https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/T3HYc0tf/images/eccd047472667c5ef520a8ae60d88fea76d07ab8.png","Skeleton","A skeleton running through the screen","2026-03-10T08:18:37.028583Z",1380877,"t54OllTX",{"hits":32670,"offset":30075,"limit":29993,"total_hits":32735},[32671,32689,32715],{"project_id":32672,"project_type":31,"slug":32673,"author":32674,"author_id":32675,"organization":3592,"organization_id":3592,"title":32676,"description":32677,"categories":32678,"display_categories":32679,"versions":32680,"downloads":32681,"follows":32682,"icon_url":32683,"date_created":32684,"date_modified":32685,"latest_version":32686,"license":29963,"client_side":29950,"server_side":30037,"gallery":32687,"featured_gallery":3592,"color":32688},"WhbRG4iK","fallingleaves","Fourmisain","INxNlPeV","Falling Leaves","Adds a neat little particle effect to leaf blocks",[100,346],[100,346],[1541,1508,1502,1490,1469,1394,1376,1361,1313,1298,1271,1214,1181,1172,113